00:23:58,225 --> 00:23:59,905
<font color="#ffffff">Fresh blood.</font>

380
00:24:18,545 --> 00:24:20,665
<font color="#ffff00">Help us.</font>

381
00:24:26,745 --> 00:24:28,265
<font color="#ffff00">Hello?</font>

382
00:24:45,105 --> 00:24:46,343
<font color="#ffffff">GIGGLES</font>

383
00:24:46,345 --> 00:24:48,503
<font color="#ffff00">Hello?</font>

384
00:24:48,505 --> 00:24:50,983
<font color="#ffff00">Hello? Excuse me?</font>

385
00:24:50,985 --> 00:24:52,385
<font color="#ffff00">Please! I-I intend you no harm.</font>

386
00:24:56,265 --> 00:25:00,945
<font color="#ffff00">However fleeting the sight, surely</font>
<font color="#ffff00">this was proof that I wasn't going</font>
<font color="#ffff00">mad?</font>

387
00:25:08,185 --> 00:25:10,585
<font color="#ffffff">WIND HOWLS</font>

388
00:25:11,945 --> 00:25:14,705
<font color="#ffffff">THUNDER RUMBLES</font>

389
00:25:24,825 --> 00:25:26,425
<font color="#ffff00">Count Dracula.</font>

390
00:25:29,305 --> 00:25:31,583
<font color="#ffff00">Are we alone in this castle?</font>

391
00:25:31,585 --> 00:25:32,905
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

392
00:25:34,265 --> 00:25:36,225
<font color="#ffffff">Except for the servants, of course.</font>

393
00:25:37,545 --> 00:25:39,503
<font color="#ffff00">I never see any servants.</font>

394
00:25:39,505 --> 00:25:41,543
<font color="#ffffff">They aren't here at night.</font>

395
00:25:41,545 --> 00:25:44,505
<font color="#ffff00">I don't see them in the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">daytime...either.</font>

396
00:25:46,945 --> 00:25:49,905
<font color="#ffff00">In fact, apart from the driver...</font>

397
00:25:52,105 --> 00:25:55,223
<font color="#ffff00">...I haven't seen anyone</font>
<font color="#ffff00">working here at all.</font>

398
00:25:55,225 --> 00:25:56,825
<font color="#ffffff">DRACULA CHUCKLES</font>

399
00:25:57,865 --> 00:25:58,945
<font color="#ffffff">Ah, yes.</font>

400
00:25:59,945 --> 00:26:00,985
<font color="#ffffff">The driver.</font>

401
00:26:07,305 --> 00:26:10,985
<font color="#ffff00">What I'm asking is,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">aside from yourself...</font>

402
00:26:13,065 --> 00:26:15,265
<font color="#ffff00">..is there anyone living in this</font>
<font color="#ffff00">castle?</font>

403
00:26:24,465 --> 00:26:25,943
<font color="#ffffff">No.</font>

404
00:26:25,945 --> 00:26:27,145
<font color="#ffffff">Jonathan...</font>

405
00:26:28,505 --> 00:26:31,625
<font color="#ffffff">...there's no-one living here.</font>

406
00:26:48,065 --> 00:26:52,665
<font color="#ffffff">SISTER AGATHA: </font><font color="#00ffff">So after sundown each</font>
<font color="#00ffff">day, Dracula appeared stronger and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">younger...</font>

407
00:26:54,065 --> 00:26:56,105
<font color="#00ffff">..while the opposite was true for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you.</font>

408
00:27:04,465 --> 00:27:07,663
<font color="#ffffff">BELL CHIMES</font>

409
00:27:07,665 --> 00:27:10,543
<font color="#00ffff">Did you understand</font>
<font color="#00ffff">what was happening to you?</font>

410
00:27:10,545 --> 00:27:13,143
<font color="#ffffff">THUD AND BIRD FLUTTERS</font>

411
00:27:13,145 --> 00:27:14,463
<font color="#ffffff">PIGEONS COO OUTSIDE</font>

412
00:27:14,465 --> 00:27:16,983
<font color="#ffff00">No. Not then.</font>

413
00:27:16,985 --> 00:27:21,623
<font color="#ffff00">I thought I was sick. Just...sick.</font>

414
00:27:21,625 --> 00:27:23,305
<font color="#00ffff">Turn your head to the side.</font>

415
00:27:24,345 --> 00:27:26,463
<font color="#ffff00">Why?</font>

416
00:27:26,465 --> 00:27:27,625
<font color="#00ffff">Show me.</font>

417
00:27:34,745 --> 00:27:38,303
<font color="#00ffff">You have been very strong,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Harker.</font>

418
00:27:38,305 --> 00:27:41,823
<font color="#00ffff">In your circumstances, I don't think</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I could have been half so brave.</font>

419
00:27:41,825 --> 00:27:42,983
<font color="#ffff00">I wasn't brave.</font>

420
00:27:42,985 --> 00:27:46,063
<font color="#ffff00">In what way was I brave?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You were trapped in that place,</font>

421
00:27:46,065 --> 00:27:48,823
<font color="#00ff00">you were afraid, and yet you spent</font>
<font color="#00ff00">your days searching the castle</font>

422
00:27:48,825 --> 00:27:50,863
<font color="#00ff00">because you thought</font>
<font color="#00ff00">someone needed your help.</font>

423
00:27:50,865 --> 00:27:53,303
<font color="#ffff00">Well, my help had been requested.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It...</font>

424
00:27:53,305 --> 00:27:55,863
<font color="#ffff00">It would have been difficult</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to refuse that.</font>

425
00:27:55,865 --> 00:27:57,023
<font color="#00ff00">Difficult?</font>

426
00:27:57,025 --> 00:27:58,905
<font color="#ffff00">Unacceptable.</font>

427
00:28:02,185 --> 00:28:04,065
<font color="#00ffff">So your search continued.</font>

428
00:28:05,145 --> 00:28:06,345
<font color="#00ffff">Tell us.</font>

429
00:28:09,785 --> 00:28:11,705
<font color="#ffffff">PANTS</font>

430
00:28:12,945 --> 00:28:18,025
<font color="#ffff00">My every exploration led me deeper</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and deeper into the labyrinth.</font>

431
00:28:34,105 --> 00:28:37,985
<font color="#ffff00">Eventually, I made a remarkable</font>
<font color="#ffff00">discovery.</font>

432
00:29:01,985 --> 00:29:03,665
<font color="#ffffff">STRAINS</font>

433
00:29:11,865 --> 00:29:15,183
<font color="#ffff00">What had become of these people?</font>

434
00:29:15,185 --> 00:29:17,665
<font color="#ffff00">Were they my predecessors?</font>

435
00:29:18,785 --> 00:29:20,625
<font color="#ffffff">GRUNTS</font>

436
00:29:23,185 --> 00:29:24,265
<font color="#ffffff">SQUEAKS</font>

437
00:29:25,545 --> 00:29:27,703
<font color="#ffffff">FLIES SWARM AND BUZZ</font>

438
00:29:27,705 --> 00:29:29,265
<font color="#ffffff">GROANS</font>

439
00:29:42,465 --> 00:29:44,465
<font color="#ffffff">LOW GURGLING</font>

440
00:29:47,865 --> 00:29:50,265
<font color="#ffffff">GURGLING CONTINUES</font>

441
00:29:51,825 --> 00:29:53,263
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

442
00:29:53,265 --> 00:29:54,463
<font color="#ffffff">EXCLAIMS</font>

443
00:29:54,465 --> 00:29:56,785
<font color="#ffffff">GURGLING INTENSIFIES</font>

444
00:29:58,265 --> 00:29:59,665
<font color="#ffffff">SQUELCHING</font>

445
00:30:01,745 --> 00:30:02,985
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER GASPS</font>

446
00:30:08,625 --> 00:30:10,583
<font color="#ffffff">SQUELCHING</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Omoara ma!</font>

447
00:30:10,585 --> 00:30:12,345
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER GASPS</font>

448
00:30:14,745 --> 00:30:16,463
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMS</font>

449
00:30:16,465 --> 00:30:19,063
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

450
00:30:19,065 --> 00:30:21,223
<font color="#00ff00">Omoara ma...</font>

451
00:30:21,225 --> 00:30:23,505
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMS</font>

452
00:30:27,905 --> 00:30:29,303
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER PANTS</font>

453
00:30:29,305 --> 00:30:31,305
<font color="#ffffff">WHEEZING: </font><font color="#00ff00">Omoara ma...</font>

454
00:30:33,545 --> 00:30:35,105
<font color="#ffffff">BONES CRUNCH</font>

455
00:30:39,065 --> 00:30:40,223
<font color="#00ff00">Omoara ma!</font>

456
00:30:40,225 --> 00:30:41,505
<font color="#ffffff">BONES CRUNCH</font>

457
00:30:48,825 --> 00:30:50,143
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS WHEEZILY</font>

458
00:30:50,145 --> 00:30:51,823
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

459
00:30:51,825 --> 00:30:54,223
<font color="#ffffff">ALL: </font><font color="#00ff00">Omoara ma!</font>

460
00:30:54,225 --> 00:30:56,265
<font color="#00ff00">Omoara ma!</font>

461
00:30:58,185 --> 00:31:01,225
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER SHRIEKS AND GASPS</font>

462
00:31:04,425 --> 00:31:07,383
<font color="#ffffff">SHOUTING ECHOES</font>

463
00:31:07,385 --> 00:31:08,663
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

464
00:31:08,665 --> 00:31:09,905
<font color="#ffffff">SHOUTING FADES</font>

465
00:31:28,785 --> 00:31:30,625
<font color="#ffffff">BAT SQUEAKS AND</font>
<font color="#ffffff">HE GASPS</font>

466
00:32:05,505 --> 00:32:07,825
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

467
00:32:18,185 --> 00:32:19,503
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMS</font>

468
00:32:19,505 --> 00:32:20,703
<font color="#ffffff">GROWLS</font>

469
00:32:20,705 --> 00:32:22,383
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER SCREAMS</font>

470
00:32:22,385 --> 00:32:23,505
<font color="#ffffff">BELL CHIMES</font>

471
00:32:30,385 --> 00:32:32,343
<font color="#ffff00">It's all I remember.</font>

472
00:32:32,345 --> 00:32:34,423
<font color="#ffff00">I fear I may have passed out.</font>

473
00:32:34,425 --> 00:32:36,143
<font color="#00ffff">Quite understandable.</font>

474
00:32:36,145 --> 00:32:38,583
<font color="#00ffff">"Omoara ma."</font>

475
00:32:38,585 --> 00:32:40,225
<font color="#00ffff">Do you know what that is?</font>

476
00:32:41,665 --> 00:32:43,383
<font color="#ffff00">It sounded like a curse.</font>

477
00:32:43,385 --> 00:32:44,743
<font color="#00ffff">It's Romanian.</font>

478
00:32:44,745 --> 00:32:46,303
<font color="#00ffff">It means "kill me".</font>

479
00:32:46,305 --> 00:32:48,103
<font color="#ffff00">They looked dead already.</font>

480
00:32:48,105 --> 00:32:49,905
<font color="#ffff00">Dead and walking.</font>

481
00:32:51,065 --> 00:32:52,225
<font color="#00ffff">Undead.</font>

482
00:32:55,265 --> 00:32:56,545
<font color="#ffff00">Tell me.</font>

483
00:33:00,225 --> 00:33:02,983
<font color="#00ffff">There is a contagion,</font>

484
00:33:02,985 --> 00:33:06,983
<font color="#00ffff">a corruption, passing through this</font>
<font color="#00ffff">world from one sufferer to the next.</font>

485
00:33:06,985 --> 00:33:11,783
<font color="#00ffff">For those unfortunate to fall victim</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to it, life becomes incurable.</font>

486
00:33:11,785 --> 00:33:15,343
<font color="#00ffff">They lose the divine ability to die.</font>

487
00:33:15,345 --> 00:33:17,143
<font color="#00ffff">As their bodies rot,</font>

488
00:33:17,145 --> 00:33:19,065
<font color="#00ffff">their consciousness persists.</font>

489
00:33:20,265 --> 00:33:22,505
<font color="#00ffff">Even as dust, their pain goes on.</font>

490
00:33:24,145 --> 00:33:27,303
<font color="#00ffff">It is a secret every gravedigger</font>
<font color="#00ffff">keeps.</font>

491
00:33:27,305 --> 00:33:28,623
<font color="#00ffff">There are those among us</font>

492
00:33:28,625 --> 00:33:31,745
<font color="#00ffff">destined to scratch at our coffin</font>
<font color="#00ffff">lids for all eternity.</font>

493
00:33:34,265 --> 00:33:37,625
<font color="#00ffff">If you work among the dead,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it's not death you fear.</font>

494
00:33:40,785 --> 00:33:42,425
<font color="#00ffff">It's the alternative.</font>

495
00:33:46,665 --> 00:33:49,343
<font color="#ffff00">Is there any salvation for such</font>
<font color="#ffff00">creatures?</font>

496
00:33:49,345 --> 00:33:51,663
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Have faith!</font>

497
00:33:51,665 --> 00:33:55,265
<font color="#00ffff">Faith is a sleeping draught</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for children and simpletons.</font>

498
00:33:56,585 --> 00:33:59,945
<font color="#00ffff">What we must have is a plan.</font>

499
00:34:01,065 --> 00:34:03,625
<font color="#ffff00">Dracula's one of them, isn't he?</font>

500
00:34:04,625 --> 00:34:06,063
<font color="#ffff00">Undead?</font>

501
00:34:06,065 --> 00:34:10,305
<font color="#00ffff">Undead certainly but, from your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">account, I think he is much more</font>
<font color="#00ffff">complicated.</font>

502
00:34:20,585 --> 00:34:22,225
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

503
00:34:26,185 --> 00:34:28,825
<font color="#ffffff">GROANS SOFTLY</font>

504
00:34:30,065 --> 00:34:31,783
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny.</font>

505
00:34:31,785 --> 00:34:33,423
<font color="#ffffff">There you are.</font>

506
00:34:33,425 --> 00:34:36,063
<font color="#ffffff">Thought we'd lost you.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Hmm...</font>

507
00:34:36,065 --> 00:34:37,783
<font color="#ffff00">What am I doing here?</font>

508
00:34:37,785 --> 00:34:41,585
<font color="#ffffff">I found you downstairs,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">asleep on the floor.</font>

509
00:34:44,705 --> 00:34:48,783
<font color="#ffffff">I could be wrong, but I think you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">were having a nightmare.</font>

510
00:34:48,785 --> 00:34:50,105
<font color="#ffffff">You do look rather pale.</font>

511
00:34:55,425 --> 00:34:56,543
<font color="#ffff00">You said you didn't drink.</font>

512
00:34:56,545 --> 00:34:58,103
<font color="#ffffff">Wine.</font>

513
00:34:58,105 --> 00:35:01,025
<font color="#ffffff">Now...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">CLEARS HIS THROAT: ..listen.</font>

514
00:35:02,065 --> 00:35:04,625
<font color="#ffffff">I need you to do something.</font>

515
00:35:05,865 --> 00:35:08,663
<font color="#ffffff">Set yourself down. There you go.</font>

516
00:35:08,665 --> 00:35:10,703
<font color="#ffffff">That's the ticket.</font>

517
00:35:10,705 --> 00:35:12,503
<font color="#ffffff">Now, take this.</font>

518
00:35:12,505 --> 00:35:16,303
<font color="#ffffff">I need you to write three letters.</font>

519
00:35:16,305 --> 00:35:18,023
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

520
00:35:18,025 --> 00:35:19,343
<font color="#ffff00">What was that?</font>

521
00:35:19,345 --> 00:35:21,303
<font color="#ffffff">That's nothing.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Sounded like a baby.</font>

522
00:35:21,305 --> 00:35:23,423
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHS: No, no, no.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">There's no baby.</font>

523
00:35:23,425 --> 00:35:25,863
<font color="#ffffff">Now, Johnny, Johnny...concentrate.</font>

524
00:35:25,865 --> 00:35:27,183
<font color="#ffffff">Three letters.</font>

525
00:35:27,185 --> 00:35:29,783
<font color="#ffff00">No-one calls me Johnny.</font>

526
00:35:29,785 --> 00:35:31,383
<font color="#ffffff">No-one?</font>

527
00:35:31,385 --> 00:35:32,425
<font color="#ffff00">No-one.</font>

528
00:35:35,185 --> 00:35:38,103
<font color="#ffffff">Company for you while you work.</font>

529
00:35:38,105 --> 00:35:40,023
<font color="#ffff00">Who is she?</font>

530
00:35:40,025 --> 00:35:41,145
<font color="#ffffff">Don't you recognise her?</font>

531
00:35:42,345 --> 00:35:44,303
<font color="#ffff00">Why would I?</font>

532
00:35:44,305 --> 00:35:46,943
<font color="#ffffff">I took it from your room. It's Mina.</font>

533
00:35:46,945 --> 00:35:48,385
<font color="#ffffff">Your fiancee.</font>

534
00:35:49,945 --> 00:35:51,185
<font color="#ffffff">Mina Murray.</font>

535
00:35:59,385 --> 00:36:01,065
<font color="#ffffff">RETCHES</font>

536
00:36:04,105 --> 00:36:06,225
<font color="#ffff00">How can I not recognise her face?</font>

537
00:36:07,265 --> 00:36:11,265
<font color="#ffffff">Well, you do look rather...drained.</font>

538
00:36:12,265 --> 00:36:13,345
<font color="#ffff00">You look young.</font>

539
00:36:16,065 --> 00:36:18,305
<font color="#ffffff">And I owe it all to you.</font>

540
00:36:19,665 --> 00:36:21,663
<font color="#ffffff">Thanks.</font>

541
00:36:21,665 --> 00:36:23,983
<font color="#ffffff">Now, it's almost time for you to go.</font>

542
00:36:23,985 --> 00:36:26,583
<font color="#ffffff">So, three letters, all to Mina.</font>

543
00:36:26,585 --> 00:36:29,583
<font color="#ffffff">The first saying you have nearly</font>
<font color="#ffffff">finished your work here</font>

544
00:36:29,585 --> 00:36:32,223
<font color="#ffffff">and will be leaving within the week.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">The second saying</font>

545
00:36:32,225 --> 00:36:36,743
<font color="#ffffff">that you have now completed your</font>
<font color="#ffffff">work and will be leaving the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">following day.</font>

546
00:36:36,745 --> 00:36:39,183
<font color="#ffffff">And the third saying</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you have now left the castle</font>

547
00:36:39,185 --> 00:36:43,143
<font color="#ffffff">and have arrived safely in...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What shall we say?</font>

548
00:36:43,145 --> 00:36:44,743
<font color="#ffffff">...Bistritz, hm?</font>

549
00:36:44,745 --> 00:36:47,383
<font color="#ffffff">I will send the letters</font>
<font color="#ffffff">at the appropriate times.</font>

550
00:36:47,385 --> 00:36:51,063
<font color="#ffffff">I'll forward the last one to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Bistritz so it can be sent from</font>
<font color="#ffffff">there.</font>

551
00:36:51,065 --> 00:36:53,623
<font color="#ffff00">Wh-why... Why would I...</font>

552
00:36:53,625 --> 00:36:55,183
<font color="#ffff00">Why would I do that?</font>

553
00:36:55,185 --> 00:36:57,743
<font color="#ffffff">So that Mina will know</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that you're coming home.</font>

554
00:36:57,745 --> 00:37:01,023
<font color="#ffff00">But why would I write the letters</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in advance?</font>

555
00:37:01,025 --> 00:37:03,423
<font color="#ffffff">Because the post here is very</font>
<font color="#ffffff">erratic.</font>

556
00:37:03,425 --> 00:37:05,583
<font color="#ffffff">It's a precaution.</font>

557
00:37:05,585 --> 00:37:08,623
<font color="#ffff00">For whom? If...</font>

558
00:37:08,625 --> 00:37:12,023
<font color="#ffff00">If something were to happen to me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and those letters had already been</font>
<font color="#ffff00">sent...</font>

559
00:37:12,025 --> 00:37:15,425
<font color="#ffffff">Then Mina wouldn't think</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to come looking for you here.</font>

560
00:37:18,785 --> 00:37:21,345
<font color="#ffffff">Do you want her to come here?</font>

561
00:37:24,545 --> 00:37:26,663
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

562
00:37:26,665 --> 00:37:28,783
<font color="#ffff00">That's a baby.</font>

563
00:37:28,785 --> 00:37:32,345
<font color="#ffff00">I can hear it crying.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">There is no baby!</font>

564
00:37:33,585 --> 00:37:36,903
<font color="#ffffff">Write the letters</font>
<font color="#ffffff">or don't write the letters.</font>

565
00:37:36,905 --> 00:37:38,583
<font color="#ffffff">It's up to you.</font>

566
00:37:38,585 --> 00:37:40,023
<font color="#ffffff">I'm only thinking about Mina.</font>

567
00:37:40,025 --> 00:37:41,103
<font color="#ffffff">SOBS</font>

568
00:37:41,105 --> 00:37:43,783
<font color="#ffffff">Now, if you don't mind. Things to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">do. See you tomorrow evening.</font>

569
00:37:43,785 --> 00:37:45,505
<font color="#ffffff">Leave the letters on the table.</font>

570
00:37:46,625 --> 00:37:48,745
<font color="#ffff00">The dates! The dates!</font>

571
00:37:50,945 --> 00:37:53,823
<font color="#ffff00">The dates for the letters...</font>

572
00:37:53,825 --> 00:37:54,865
<font color="#ffff00">How should I date them?</font>

573
00:37:56,145 --> 00:37:58,783
<font color="#ffffff">Well, let's see. Er...</font>

574
