587
00:38:32,305 --> 00:38:34,745
<font color="#ffffff">No-one is stopping you.</font>

588
00:38:36,545 --> 00:38:38,383
<font color="#ffff00">I don't have the strength.</font>

589
00:38:38,385 --> 00:38:40,823
<font color="#ffffff">No. I know.</font>

590
00:38:40,825 --> 00:38:44,463
<font color="#ffffff">It's not your fault, Johnny.</font>
