597
00:39:01,705 --> 00:39:03,705
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

598
00:39:06,465 --> 00:39:09,383
<font color="#ffff00">I knew in that moment that I had a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">choice.</font>

599
00:39:09,385 --> 00:39:11,623
<font color="#ffff00">I'd been told the span of my life,</font>

600
00:39:11,625 --> 00:39:14,145
<font color="#ffff00">the limit of my existence - the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">29th.</font>

601
00:39:15,625 --> 00:39:19,543
<font color="#ffff00">Now, I could stay here, dying piece</font>
<font color="#ffff00">by piece, till I found myself</font>

602
00:39:19,545 --> 00:39:21,985
<font color="#ffff00">nailed into one of those boxes.</font>

603
00:39:25,385 --> 00:39:26,905
<font color="#00ffff">Or...?</font>

604
00:39:27,945 --> 00:39:30,585
<font color="#ffff00">Or I could kill Count Dracula.</font>

605
00:39:32,305 --> 00:39:35,183
<font color="#00ffff">Not an easy task in the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">circumstances.</font>

606
00:39:35,185 --> 00:39:38,103
<font color="#ffff00">No, but I had certain advantages.</font>

607
00:39:38,105 --> 00:39:41,103
<font color="#00ffff">I should be fascinated to know</font>
<font color="#00ffff">what they were.</font>

608
00:39:41,105 --> 00:39:43,303
<font color="#ffff00">I was enfeebled and trapped...</font>

609
00:39:43,305 --> 00:39:45,903
<font color="#00ffff">Well, indeed.</font>

610
00:39:45,905 --> 00:39:47,943
<font color="#ffff00">..so Dracula did not consider me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a threat.</font>

611
00:39:47,945 --> 00:39:49,823
<font color="#00ffff">That's true, yes.</font>

612
00:39:49,825 --> 00:39:52,785
<font color="#00ffff">But, on the negative side,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you were enfeebled and trapped.</font>

613
00:39:54,785 --> 00:39:56,623
<font color="#ffff00">I had a potential ally.</font>

614
00:39:56,625 --> 00:39:59,103
<font color="#ffff00">One who could climb the castle</font>
<font color="#ffff00">walls.</font>

615
00:39:59,105 --> 00:40:01,263
<font color="#00ffff">One you couldn't even find?</font>

616
00:40:01,265 --> 00:40:04,065
<font color="#ffff00">That was because I was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">looking for the wrong thing.</font>

617
00:40:05,345 --> 00:40:07,583
<font color="#ffff00">I should have been looking for a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">map.</font>

618
00:40:07,585 --> 00:40:09,903
<font color="#00ffff">Of the castle? But there wasn't one.</font>

619
00:40:09,905 --> 00:40:11,943
<font color="#ffff00">That's what Dracula believed.</font>

620
00:40:11,945 --> 00:40:14,583
<font color="#ffff00">But, in telling me that,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he'd also told me where to find it.</font>

621
00:40:14,585 --> 00:40:16,343
<font color="#00ffff">What did he say?</font>

622
00:40:16,345 --> 00:40:17,385
<font color="#ffff00">I told you.</font>

623
00:40:20,385 --> 00:40:21,463
<font color="#00ffff">I missed it.</font>

624
00:40:21,465 --> 00:40:23,183
<font color="#ffff00">You did.</font>

625
00:40:23,185 --> 00:40:25,463
<font color="#00ffff">Then you're much quicker than me.</font>

626
00:40:25,465 --> 00:40:28,785
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not quick.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I've always been slow.</font>

627
00:40:29,785 --> 00:40:32,863
<font color="#ffff00">But the thing is, when you're slow,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you know you need to pay attention.</font>

628
00:40:32,865 --> 00:40:35,663
<font color="#ffff00">It's the clever ones who never</font>
<font color="#ffff00">listen.</font>

629
00:40:35,665 --> 00:40:38,023
<font color="#ffff00">You've read all this.</font>

630
00:40:38,025 --> 00:40:39,825
<font color="#ffff00">Already. In my account.</font>

631
00:40:41,185 --> 00:40:44,625
<font color="#00ffff">It's vague in certain crucial</font>
<font color="#00ffff">regards.</font>

632
00:40:46,345 --> 00:40:48,505
<font color="#00ffff">Continue, please.</font>

633
00:40:49,745 --> 00:40:51,543
<font color="#ffff00">It occurred to me that night</font>

634
00:40:51,545 --> 00:40:54,225
<font color="#ffff00">that Dracula said more than he</font>
<font color="#ffff00">intended.</font>

635
00:40:55,625 --> 00:40:57,705
<font color="#ffff00">And more than he knew.</font>

636
00:41:01,785 --> 00:41:03,663
<font color="#ffff00">As he was a creature of the night,</font>

637
00:41:03,665 --> 00:41:06,503
<font color="#ffff00">I had to wait until morning</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to test my theory.</font>

638
00:41:06,505 --> 00:41:08,345
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

639
00:41:15,305 --> 00:41:19,783
<font color="#ffff00">The Count said there was no map,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but Petruvio was an artist,</font>

640
00:41:19,785 --> 00:41:22,225
<font color="#ffff00">and artists always wish to be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">understood.</font>

641
00:41:24,505 --> 00:41:28,143
<font color="#ffff00">The castle was a monument</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the architect's lost love</font>

642
00:41:28,145 --> 00:41:30,745
<font color="#ffff00">and the sunlight</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to which he would never return.</font>

643
00:41:32,905 --> 00:41:35,343
<font color="#ffff00">And what else is sunlight...</font>

644
00:41:35,345 --> 00:41:37,545
<font color="#ffff00">..but the face of one's beloved?</font>

645
00:41:40,185 --> 00:41:42,745
<font color="#ffff00">The path to the sunlight.</font>

646
00:41:56,585 --> 00:41:58,343
<font color="#ffff00">It was clear from the castle maps</font>

647
00:41:58,345 --> 00:42:01,903
<font color="#ffff00">that Petruvio had created</font>
<font color="#ffff00">within his design</font>

648
00:42:01,905 --> 00:42:03,943
<font color="#ffff00">a system of short cuts through the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">maze.</font>

649
00:42:03,945 --> 00:42:07,263
<font color="#ffff00">Hidden passages, possibly unknown</font>

650
00:42:07,265 --> 00:42:09,065
<font color="#ffff00">even to Dracula himself.</font>

651
00:42:30,265 --> 00:42:33,665
<font color="#ffff00">How many times had I looked</font>
<font color="#ffff00">at that picture and not seen it?</font>

652
00:42:35,825 --> 00:42:38,705
<font color="#ffff00">Petruvio's wife was the sunlight...</font>

653
00:42:39,985 --> 00:42:42,865
<font color="#ffff00">..and he stood guard at the door.</font>

