00:43:51,985 --> 00:43:53,305
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

663
00:43:55,385 --> 00:43:57,183
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

664
00:43:57,185 --> 00:43:59,263
<font color="#ffffff">SQUEAKING</font>

665
00:43:59,265 --> 00:44:00,625
<font color="#ffffff">CLATTERING</font>

666
00:44:18,145 --> 00:44:22,703
<font color="#00ff00">He doesn't know I can get out of the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">box. Don't tell him.</font>

667
00:44:22,705 --> 00:44:24,583
<font color="#ffff00">I won't.</font>

668
00:44:24,585 --> 00:44:27,143
<font color="#00ff00">Are you his friend now?</font>

669
00:44:27,145 --> 00:44:28,503
<font color="#ffff00">No. I, er...</font>

670
00:44:28,505 --> 00:44:29,783
<font color="#ffff00">I-I...</font>

671
00:44:29,785 --> 00:44:31,225
<font color="#ffff00">..I work for him.</font>

672
00:44:32,225 --> 00:44:33,303
<font color="#ffff00">I'm a lawyer.</font>

673
00:44:33,305 --> 00:44:35,903
<font color="#ffff00">From England.</font>

674
00:44:35,905 --> 00:44:38,385
<font color="#00ff00">I think he's made you his friend.</font>

675
00:44:39,585 --> 00:44:40,665
<font color="#ffff00">Why?</font>

676
00:44:42,625 --> 00:44:44,583
<font color="#00ff00">What's England?</font>

677
00:44:44,585 --> 00:44:47,383
<font color="#ffff00">It's where I'm from.</font>

678
00:44:47,385 --> 00:44:48,863
<font color="#ffff00">You know it.</font>

679
00:44:48,865 --> 00:44:51,663
<font color="#ffff00">You're...speaking English.</font>

680
00:44:51,665 --> 00:44:53,223
<font color="#00ff00">I learnt it.</font>

681
00:44:53,225 --> 00:44:54,383
<font color="#ffffff">SHE LAUGHS</font>

682
00:44:54,385 --> 00:44:56,625
<font color="#ffff00">How?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">It tasted fun.</font>

683
00:44:58,345 --> 00:44:59,623
<font color="#ffff00">Tasted?</font>

684
00:44:59,625 --> 00:45:03,305
<font color="#00ff00">Once you are the Count's friend,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">all languages are the same.</font>

685
00:45:06,825 --> 00:45:08,625
<font color="#00ff00">I'm hungry.</font>

686
00:45:09,665 --> 00:45:11,903
<font color="#ffff00">Was it you at the window?</font>

687
00:45:11,905 --> 00:45:14,463
<font color="#ffff00">You left the message?</font>

688
00:45:14,465 --> 00:45:17,063
<font color="#00ff00">I smelt you.</font>

689
00:45:17,065 --> 00:45:19,023
<font color="#ffff00">You're trapped here.</font>

690
00:45:19,025 --> 00:45:22,343
<font color="#00ff00">You're trapped too.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I want to help you.</font>

691
00:45:22,345 --> 00:45:24,343
<font color="#00ff00">Tell him I'm hungry!</font>

692
00:45:24,345 --> 00:45:26,305
<font color="#00ff00">He only gives me scraps.</font>

693
00:45:27,345 --> 00:45:28,985
<font color="#00ff00">Tiny little things.</font>

694
00:45:30,265 --> 00:45:32,425
<font color="#00ff00">Tell him I finished the last one.</font>

695
00:45:33,625 --> 00:45:35,545
<font color="#00ff00">I finished it really quickly.</font>

696
00:45:36,865 --> 00:45:39,063
<font color="#00ff00">I'm hungry!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Agh!</font>

697
00:45:39,065 --> 00:45:40,503
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GROWLS</font>

698
00:45:40,505 --> 00:45:43,223
<font color="#ffff00">Look at it!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Look at it!</font>

699
00:45:43,225 --> 00:45:44,705
<font color="#ffff00">It is the sign of the cross.</font>

700
00:45:45,825 --> 00:45:47,263
<font color="#ffff00">The symbol of our Lord.</font>

701
00:45:47,265 --> 00:45:48,825
<font color="#00ff00">I know.</font>

702
00:45:50,545 --> 00:45:51,825
<font color="#00ff00">It's pretty.</font>

703
00:45:58,625 --> 00:46:00,425
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMS ECHO</font>

704
00:46:02,185 --> 00:46:07,185
<font color="#00ffff">You assumed, I suppose,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that the cross would ward off evil.</font>

705
00:46:08,905 --> 00:46:10,463
<font color="#ffff00">Why are you smiling?</font>

706
00:46:10,465 --> 00:46:14,743
<font color="#00ffff">Your faith. I think it's touching.</font>

707
00:46:14,745 --> 00:46:16,823
<font color="#ffff00">What happened to yours?</font>

708
00:46:16,825 --> 00:46:20,385
<font color="#00ffff">I have looked for God everywhere</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in this world and never found him.</font>

709
00:46:21,425 --> 00:46:22,583
<font color="#ffff00">Then why are you here?</font>

710
00:46:22,585 --> 00:46:25,823
<font color="#00ffff">Like many women of my age,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I'm trapped in a loveless marriage,</font>

711
00:46:25,825 --> 00:46:28,505
<font color="#00ffff">maintaining appearances</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for the sake of a roof over my head.</font>

712
00:46:29,865 --> 00:46:34,303
<font color="#00ffff">Now then, we proceed to your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">miraculous escape from</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Castle Dracula,</font>

713
00:46:34,305 --> 00:46:36,865
<font color="#00ffff">about which you have been so vague.</font>

714
00:47:07,705 --> 00:47:09,223
<font color="#ffffff">KNOCKS</font>

715
00:47:09,225 --> 00:47:12,305
<font color="#ffff00">Somebody! Please, help!</font>

716
00:47:15,705 --> 00:47:18,863
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

717
00:47:18,865 --> 00:47:20,905
<font color="#ffffff">STRAINS</font>

