00:47:22,665 --> 00:47:25,105
<font color="#ffffff">BABY GURGLES</font>

719
00:47:28,145 --> 00:47:30,145
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

720
00:47:41,225 --> 00:47:42,663
<font color="#ffffff">CRIES</font>

721
00:47:42,665 --> 00:47:44,943
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER PANTS</font>

722
00:47:44,945 --> 00:47:46,785
<font color="#ffffff">CRIES</font>

723
00:47:50,065 --> 00:47:52,225
<font color="#ffffff">GROANS</font>

724
00:47:54,585 --> 00:47:56,983
<font color="#ffffff">WHEEZES</font>

725
00:47:56,985 --> 00:47:59,783
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny, this is interesting.</font>

726
00:47:59,785 --> 00:48:04,023
<font color="#ffffff">I've never seen it work</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with a baby before. Never.</font>

727
00:48:04,025 --> 00:48:06,783
<font color="#ffffff">I think I might keep it on for a</font>
<font color="#ffffff">while.</font>

728
00:48:06,785 --> 00:48:10,065
<font color="#ffffff">I hope this doesn't mean</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that I'm getting sentimental.</font>

729
00:48:14,825 --> 00:48:18,223
<font color="#ffff00">Why did you kill her?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Who?</font>

730
00:48:18,225 --> 00:48:20,783
<font color="#ffffff">Oh. Um...</font>

731
00:48:20,785 --> 00:48:23,865
<font color="#ffffff">Because I wanted to see if she would</font>
<font color="#ffffff">die, I suppose.</font>

732
00:48:25,305 --> 00:48:28,023
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny, don't give me that look.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You were a child once.</font>

733
00:48:28,025 --> 00:48:29,343
<font color="#ffffff">You know the feeling.</font>

734
00:48:29,345 --> 00:48:32,623
<font color="#ffffff">Didn't you break your toys apart</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to see how they worked?</font>

735
00:48:32,625 --> 00:48:34,783
<font color="#ffff00">You're a monster.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">And you're a lawyer.</font>

736
00:48:34,785 --> 00:48:36,065
<font color="#ffffff">Nobody's perfect.</font>

737
00:48:37,105 --> 00:48:39,783
<font color="#ffffff">Ah, a stake through the heart.</font>

738
00:48:39,785 --> 00:48:43,623
<font color="#ffffff">You see,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">sometimes the legends are right.</font>

739
00:48:43,625 --> 00:48:46,383
<font color="#ffffff">This is not one you can test too</font>
<font color="#ffffff">often, though.</font>

740
00:48:46,385 --> 00:48:49,343
<font color="#ffffff">I only ever have three brides at a</font>
<font color="#ffffff">time.</font>

741
00:48:49,345 --> 00:48:51,183
<font color="#ffff00">"Brides"?</font>

742
00:48:51,185 --> 00:48:53,983
<font color="#ffffff">Brides, yes. I think that's the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">right word for it.</font>

743
00:48:53,985 --> 00:48:55,503
<font color="#ffffff">You see, um...</font>

744
00:48:55,505 --> 00:48:57,823
<font color="#ffffff">CLEARS HIS THROAT</font>
<font color="#ffffff">..I am trying to reproduce...</font>

745
00:48:57,825 --> 00:48:59,623
<font color="#ffffff">CRATE OPENS</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Oh!</font>

746
00:48:59,625 --> 00:49:00,903
<font color="#ffffff">SQUISHING</font>

747
00:49:00,905 --> 00:49:04,105
<font color="#ffffff">..which, frankly, can be a bit of a</font>
<font color="#ffffff">challenge when there is only one of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you.</font>

748
00:49:05,305 --> 00:49:06,783
<font color="#ffff00">Agh!</font>

749
00:49:06,785 --> 00:49:10,543
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, Johnny.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You're just about done, aren't you?</font>

750
00:49:10,545 --> 00:49:12,183
<font color="#ffffff">She was a thirsty little thing,</font>

751
00:49:12,185 --> 00:49:16,463
<font color="#ffffff">and to think that she was going to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">keep you in that box all to herself!</font>

752
00:49:16,465 --> 00:49:18,223
<font color="#ffff00">Are you going to kill me?</font>

753
00:49:18,225 --> 00:49:20,105
<font color="#ffffff">Of course I'm going to kill you.</font>

754
00:49:22,505 --> 00:49:26,345
<font color="#ffffff">Why does death always come</font>
<font color="#ffffff">as such a shock to mortals?</font>

755
00:49:34,985 --> 00:49:40,183
<font color="#ffff00">You took everything from me.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Of course I did.</font>

756
00:49:40,185 --> 00:49:44,103
<font color="#ffffff">You are the high road</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that leads me to England.</font>

757
00:49:44,105 --> 00:49:46,543
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER: </font><font color="#ffff00">Why? Why England?</font>

758
00:49:46,545 --> 00:49:47,985
<font color="#ffffff">Ah.</font>

759
00:49:49,665 --> 00:49:51,143
<font color="#ffffff">The people.</font>

760
00:49:51,145 --> 00:49:55,103
<font color="#ffffff">All those sophisticated</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and intelligent people.</font>

761
00:49:55,105 --> 00:49:58,263
<font color="#ffffff">As I've been trying to tell</font>
<font color="#ffffff">everyone for centuries,</font>

762
00:49:58,265 --> 00:50:00,183
<font color="#ffffff">you are what you eat.</font>

763
00:50:00,185 --> 00:50:02,425
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER WHIMPERS</font>

764
00:50:12,385 --> 00:50:14,665
<font color="#ffffff">WIND WHISTLES</font>

765
00:50:20,785 --> 00:50:22,105
<font color="#ffffff">Now...</font>

766
00:50:25,185 --> 00:50:29,185
<font color="#ffffff">...if you don't mind, I need you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to do one last thing for me.</font>

767
00:50:30,585 --> 00:50:33,463
<font color="#ffffff">I haven't seen her in hundreds of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">years.</font>

768
00:50:33,465 --> 00:50:35,423
<font color="#ffffff">Describe her to me.</font>

769
00:50:35,425 --> 00:50:36,863
<font color="#ffffff">WEAKLY: </font><font color="#ffff00">Who?</font>

770
00:50:36,865 --> 00:50:38,743
<font color="#ffffff">I've had artists paint her,</font>

771
00:50:38,745 --> 00:50:40,303
<font color="#ffffff">and poets capture her in words,</font>

772
00:50:40,305 --> 00:50:45,343
<font color="#ffffff">and Mozart wrote</font>
<font color="#ffffff">such a pretty little tune, I-I...</font>

773
00:50:45,345 --> 00:50:48,425
<font color="#ffffff">CLEARS HIS THROAT: ..I really</font>
<font color="#ffffff">should have spared him, but...</font>

774
00:50:49,465 --> 00:50:51,303
<font color="#ffffff">..what does a lawyer see?</font>

775
00:50:51,305 --> 00:50:53,463
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny, in my memory,</font>

776
00:50:53,465 --> 00:50:58,185
<font color="#ffffff">she sets behind the second-highest</font>
<font color="#ffffff">peak at this time of year, and she's</font>
<font color="#ffffff">quite red.</font>

777
00:51:00,625 --> 00:51:02,065
<font color="#ffffff">Is she red, Johnny?</font>

778
00:51:03,705 --> 00:51:05,823
<font color="#ffff00">Look for yourself.</font>

779
00:51:05,825 --> 00:51:08,065
<font color="#ffffff">But that will burn me to dust.</font>

780
00:51:13,945 --> 00:51:15,223
<font color="#ffff00">Good.</font>

781
00:51:15,225 --> 00:51:17,103
<font color="#ffffff">Fair enough.</font>

782
00:51:17,105 --> 00:51:19,823
<font color="#ffffff">Absolutely fair enough.</font>

783
00:51:19,825 --> 00:51:22,023
<font color="#ffff00">Will you put me in a box?</font>

784
00:51:22,025 --> 00:51:24,823
<font color="#ffffff">Keep your eyes on the sun, Johnny.</font>

785
00:51:24,825 --> 00:51:26,545
<font color="#ffffff">It'll be the last time you see her.</font>

786
00:51:28,065 --> 00:51:31,863
<font color="#ffffff">There is a box waiting for you,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in case you walk, yes,</font>

787
00:51:31,865 --> 00:51:34,103
<font color="#ffffff">but most people I feed off just die.</font>

788
00:51:34,105 --> 00:51:36,025
<font color="#ffffff">So you'll probably be fine.</font>

789
00:51:37,665 --> 00:51:39,983
<font color="#ffffff">Don't you see?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">An end is a blessing.</font>

790
00:51:39,985 --> 00:51:42,703
<font color="#ffffff">Dying gives you size.</font>

791
00:51:42,705 --> 00:51:47,343
<font color="#ffffff">It's the mountaintop from which</font>
<font color="#ffffff">your whole life is at last visible.</font>

792
00:51:47,345 --> 00:51:49,423
<font color="#ffffff">From beginning to end.</font>

793
00:51:49,425 --> 00:51:51,625
<font color="#ffffff">Death completes you.</font>

794
00:51:53,665 --> 00:51:54,903
<font color="#ffff00">Spare me.</font>

795
00:51:54,905 --> 00:51:55,983
<font color="#ffffff">How?</font>

796
00:51:55,985 --> 00:51:57,623
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHS</font>

797
00:51:57,625 --> 00:52:00,943
<font color="#ffffff">Answer me. Johnny, how?</font>

798
00:52:00,945 --> 00:52:02,665
<font color="#ffffff">How do I spare you?</font>

799
00:52:04,065 --> 00:52:06,465
<font color="#00ffff">How indeed, Mr Harker?</font>

800
00:52:07,505 --> 00:52:09,183
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Harker?</font>

801
00:52:09,185 --> 00:52:10,303
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Harker...</font>

802
00:52:10,305 --> 00:52:11,383
<font color="#ffffff">BELL CHIMES</font>

803
00:52:11,385 --> 00:52:14,465
<font color="#00ffff">..you were about to explain</font>
<font color="#00ffff">how you escaped from the castle.</font>

804
00:52:18,265 --> 00:52:19,743
<font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

805
00:52:19,745 --> 00:52:22,143
<font color="#ffff00">Y-you've read my account.</font>

806
00:52:22,145 --> 00:52:23,543
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

807
00:52:23,545 --> 00:52:25,825
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps it will help</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to refresh your memory.</font>

808
00:52:40,545 --> 00:52:42,905
<font color="#ffff00">"Dracula will be served."</font>

809
00:52:44,465 --> 00:52:45,505
<font color="#ffff00">What is this?</font>

810
00:52:46,665 --> 00:52:49,985
<font color="#ffff00">"Dracula is my master.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Dracula will be obeyed. Dra...</font>

811
00:52:51,545 --> 00:52:53,463
<font color="#ffff00">"Dracula is the beginning and the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">end.</font>

812
00:52:53,465 --> 00:52:56,625
<font color="#ffff00">"Dracula is all things. Dracula is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">God." What?</font>

813
00:52:57,825 --> 00:52:59,303
<font color="#ffff00">I-I didn't write this.</font>

814
00:52:59,305 --> 00:53:02,583
<font color="#00ffff">When you were first brought here,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you asked for a pen and paper.</font>

815
00:53:02,585 --> 00:53:06,183
<font color="#00ffff">You were up all day and all night,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and this is what you wrote.</font>

816
00:53:06,185 --> 00:53:09,503
<font color="#ffff00">No, no, no, no, no.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I-I thought I'd...</font>

817
00:53:09,505 --> 00:53:12,463
<font color="#00ffff">You thought you'd written an account</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of your stay at Castle Dracula.</font>

818
00:53:12,465 --> 00:53:15,865
<font color="#00ffff">The only account you've given is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the account you're giving right now.</font>

819
00:53:23,985 --> 00:53:26,345
<font color="#00ffff">It's time to finish your story.</font>

820
00:53:29,585 --> 00:53:32,743
<font color="#ffffff">DRACULA: Johnny, how?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">How do I spare you?</font>

821
00:53:32,745 --> 00:53:34,385
<font color="#ffffff">How?</font>

822
00:53:35,825 --> 00:53:37,143
<font color="#ffffff">WEAKLY: </font><font color="#ffff00">Let me go.</font>

823
00:53:37,145 --> 00:53:39,103
<font color="#ffffff">You know why I'm going to England.</font>

824
00:53:39,105 --> 00:53:41,063
<font color="#ffffff">You know that I'm going to kill</font>
<font color="#ffffff">people.</font>

825
00:53:41,065 --> 00:53:43,983
<font color="#ffffff">A lot of them. As many as I need.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">And perhaps even more.</font>

826
00:53:43,985 --> 00:53:45,343
<font color="#ffff00">But...</font>

827
00:53:45,345 --> 00:53:46,705
<font color="#ffffff">COUGHS</font>

828
00:53:48,425 --> 00:53:49,943
<font color="#ffff00">..I won't...</font>

829
00:53:49,945 --> 00:53:51,983
<font color="#ffffff">You won't what?</font>

830
00:53:51,985 --> 00:53:54,823
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, you won't tell anyone about me?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Or try to stop me?</font>

831
00:53:54,825 --> 00:53:56,903
<font color="#ffffff">You'll just let me slaughter all</font>

832
00:53:56,905 --> 00:53:58,543
<font color="#ffffff">those innocents, no questions asked?</font>

833
00:53:58,545 --> 00:53:59,823
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHS</font>

834
00:53:59,825 --> 00:54:02,823
<font color="#ffffff">Some lawyer you turned out to be,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny!</font>

835
00:54:02,825 --> 00:54:04,343
<font color="#ffff00">I promise.</font>

836
00:54:04,345 --> 00:54:06,183
<font color="#ffff00">I...I swe...</font>

837
00:54:06,185 --> 00:54:08,143
<font color="#ffff00">I...I swear.</font>

838
00:54:08,145 --> 00:54:09,383
<font color="#ffff00">I... I...</font>

839
00:54:09,385 --> 00:54:10,703
<font color="#ffff00">I swear.</font>

840
00:54:10,705 --> 00:54:12,025
<font color="#ffffff">All right, then.</font>

841
00:54:13,305 --> 00:54:15,103
<font color="#ffffff">Do that.</font>

842
00:54:15,105 --> 00:54:16,703
<font color="#ffffff">GASPING: </font><font color="#ffff00">What?</font>

843
00:54:16,705 --> 00:54:18,343
<font color="#ffffff">Swear.</font>

844
00:54:18,345 --> 00:54:23,743
<font color="#ffffff">I'm going to England to destroy</font>
<font color="#ffffff">everything and everyone you love,</font>

845
00:54:23,745 --> 00:54:27,385
<font color="#ffffff">but if you give me your word</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that you won't try to stop me...</font>

846
00:54:28,745 --> 00:54:29,905
<font color="#ffffff">..I'll spare you.</font>

847
00:54:31,905 --> 00:54:32,943
<font color="#ffff00">It's a trick.</font>

848
00:54:32,945 --> 00:54:34,303
<font color="#ffffff">Give me your word.</font>

849
00:54:34,305 --> 00:54:37,463
<font color="#ffffff">SOBBING: </font><font color="#ffff00">No...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">You're going to kill me anyway.</font>

850
00:54:37,465 --> 00:54:40,825
<font color="#ffffff">Look me in the eye and give me your</font>
<font color="#ffffff">word.</font>

851
00:54:47,545 --> 00:54:49,345
<font color="#ffff00">Count Dracula...</font>

852
00:54:50,785 --> 00:54:52,225
<font color="#ffff00">..I give you my word.</font>

853
00:54:54,225 --> 00:54:55,985
<font color="#ffff00">If you let me out of this place...</font>

854
00:54:58,665 --> 00:55:01,583
<font color="#ffff00">..if you let me live...</font>

855
00:55:01,585 --> 00:55:03,703
<font color="#ffff00">..then I...</font>

856
00:55:03,705 --> 00:55:07,785
<font color="#ffff00">..then I will do everything in my</font>
<font color="#ffff00">power to stop you.</font>

857
00:55:11,185 --> 00:55:12,345
<font color="#ffffff">Quite right.</font>

858
00:55:14,545 --> 00:55:16,385
<font color="#ffffff">That's my Johnny.</font>

859
00:55:17,785 --> 00:55:19,183
<font color="#ffffff">Welcome to the mountaintop.</font>

860
00:55:19,185 --> 00:55:20,665
<font color="#ffffff">BONES CRUNCH</font>

861
00:55:26,905 --> 00:55:28,383
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not breathing.</font>

862
00:55:28,385 --> 00:55:30,943
<font color="#00ffff">Sometimes you do,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but I think it's mostly habit.</font>

863
00:55:30,945 --> 00:55:33,905
<font color="#00ffff">You have no heartbeat, either.</font>

864
00:55:35,625 --> 00:55:36,783
<font color="#ffff00">I'm dead.</font>

865
00:55:36,785 --> 00:55:38,583
<font color="#00ffff">Undead.</font>

866
00:55:38,585 --> 00:55:41,305
<font color="#00ffff">But apparently, not yet a vampire.</font>

867
00:55:43,145 --> 00:55:46,145
<font color="#00ffff">One must cling on to any good news</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that there is.</font>

868
00:55:49,225 --> 00:55:51,223
<font color="#ffffff">WOLF HOWLS IN THE DISTANCE</font>

869
00:55:51,225 --> 00:55:54,103
<font color="#ffff00">I do not serve Dracula.</font>

870
00:55:54,105 --> 00:55:56,263
<font color="#00ffff">No, but he's in your mind.</font>

871
00:55:56,265 --> 00:55:59,225
<font color="#00ffff">The question is,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">why are you not in one of his boxes?</font>

872
00:56:00,505 --> 00:56:02,305
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know.</font>

873
00:56:03,345 --> 00:56:06,383
<font color="#00ffff">It's not something</font>
<font color="#00ffff">one ever anticipates asking,</font>

874
00:56:06,385 --> 00:56:08,665
<font color="#00ffff">but what happened AFTER you were</font>
<font color="#00ffff">murdered?</font>

875
00:56:23,025 --> 00:56:27,743
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, my goodness, that was quick.</font>

876
00:56:27,745 --> 00:56:29,663
<font color="#ffffff">WHEEZES AND GASPS</font>

877
00:56:29,665 --> 00:56:32,383
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny, Johnny, Johnny...</font>

878
00:56:32,385 --> 00:56:34,223
<font color="#ffffff">Usually, people have a lie-down</font>
<font color="#ffffff">first.</font>

879
00:56:34,225 --> 00:56:35,503
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

880
00:56:35,505 --> 00:56:36,865
<font color="#ffffff">DRACULA CHUCKLES</font>

881
00:56:37,985 --> 00:56:40,505
<font color="#ffffff">You're going to be a lively one,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">aren't you?</font>

882
00:56:42,985 --> 00:56:46,343
<font color="#ffffff">You came back so quickly.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">That was impressive.</font>

883
00:56:46,345 --> 00:56:49,423
<font color="#ffffff">You even have the beginnings</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of a will of your own.</font>

884
00:56:49,425 --> 00:56:53,545
<font color="#ffffff">None of the others have much</font>
<font color="#ffffff">beyond hunger, but look at you go!</font>

885
00:56:55,705 --> 00:57:00,745
<font color="#ffffff">Well, don't you see?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">This changes everything.</font>

886
00:57:01,905 --> 00:57:05,183
<font color="#ffffff">Stay. Stay!</font>

887
00:57:05,185 --> 00:57:08,065
<font color="#ffffff">You could be my finest bride.</font>

888
00:57:10,545 --> 00:57:14,783
<font color="#ffffff">The others just became beasts,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">but you've kept your spirit.</font>

889
00:57:14,785 --> 00:57:17,063
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny, you're like me.</font>

890
00:57:17,065 --> 00:57:20,783
<font color="#ffff00">I am not like you!</font>

891
00:57:20,785 --> 00:57:24,343
<font color="#ffffff">PIERCING SCREAM</font>

892
00:57:24,345 --> 00:57:27,225
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMING CONTINUES</font>

893
00:57:29,425 --> 00:57:32,065
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMING ECHOES</font>

894
00:57:35,425 --> 00:57:38,343
<font color="#ffff00">That's everything. That's...</font>

895
00:57:38,345 --> 00:57:40,663
<font color="#ffff00">That's all I remember.</font>

896
00:57:40,665 --> 00:57:42,783
<font color="#00ffff">But why did he scream?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">What did you do?</font>

897
00:57:42,785 --> 00:57:44,983
<font color="#ffff00">Nothing, I did nothing. I...</font>

898
00:57:44,985 --> 00:57:47,903
<font color="#ffff00">I looked at him, and the next thing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I remember was that I was here.</font>

899
00:57:47,905 --> 00:57:49,463
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, yes, yes, never mind that.</font>

900
00:57:49,465 --> 00:57:51,663
<font color="#00ffff">We know what happened next.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">No, I...</font>

901
00:57:51,665 --> 00:57:54,065
<font color="#ffff00">I don't... I don't remember.</font>

902
00:57:56,345 --> 00:58:01,223
<font color="#00ffff">The river bore you out to sea, and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the fishermen found you, caught in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">their net.</font>

903
00:58:01,225 --> 00:58:05,263
<font color="#00ffff">A drowned man walking and talking</font>
<font color="#00ffff">arouses a certain amount of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">curiosity,</font>

904
00:58:05,265 --> 00:58:06,503
<font color="#00ffff">and you were brought to me,</font>

905
00:58:06,505 --> 00:58:09,423
<font color="#00ffff">babbling of a girl called Mina</font>
<font color="#00ffff">whose face you had forgotten</font>

906
00:58:09,425 --> 00:58:11,543
<font color="#00ffff">and an evil count</font>
<font color="#00ffff">who had stolen your soul.</font>

907
00:58:11,545 --> 00:58:13,265
<font color="#ffff00">Why was I brought to you?</font>

908
00:58:14,865 --> 00:58:18,225
<font color="#00ffff">I am known to have some expertise in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the realm of witchcraft and the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">occult.</font>

909
00:58:19,665 --> 00:58:21,263
<font color="#ffff00">You're a nun!</font>

910
00:58:21,265 --> 00:58:23,743
<font color="#00ffff">We can discuss my imperfectly</font>
<font color="#00ffff">suppressed</font>

911
00:58:23,745 --> 00:58:26,343
<font color="#00ffff">fascination with everything dark and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">evil another time.</font>

912
00:58:26,345 --> 00:58:31,743
<font color="#00ffff">For now, we will focus</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on why Dracula screamed.</font>

913
00:58:31,745 --> 00:58:33,465
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER SIGHS</font>

914
00:58:47,745 --> 00:58:49,463
<font color="#00ffff">You were facing the sun!</font>

915
00:58:49,465 --> 00:58:51,185
<font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

916
00:58:53,065 --> 00:58:55,503
<font color="#00ffff">I have sought to find God all my</font>
<font color="#00ffff">life,</font>

917
00:58:55,505 --> 00:58:59,103
<font color="#00ffff">and never found a sign of him</font>
<font color="#00ffff">anywhere.</font>

918
00:58:59,105 --> 00:59:01,543
<font color="#00ffff">Why now? Why you? Why him?</font>

919
00:59:01,545 --> 00:59:03,343
<font color="#ffff00">I don't understand.</font>

920
00:59:03,345 --> 00:59:05,025
<font color="#00ffff">Then, think!</font>

921
00:59:15,225 --> 00:59:18,625
<font color="#00ffff">Count Dracula fears the cross.</font>

922
00:59:19,625 --> 00:59:22,743
<font color="#00ffff">He fears the symbol of our Lord.</font>

923
00:59:22,745 --> 00:59:26,143
<font color="#ffff00">The girl didn't. </font><font color="#00ffff">Never mind the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">girl. She was nothing.</font>

924
00:59:26,145 --> 00:59:31,623
<font color="#00ffff">Dracula, prince among vampires,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">fears the cross.</font>

925
00:59:31,625 --> 00:59:34,463
<font color="#00ffff">Do you understand what that means?</font>

926
00:59:34,465 --> 00:59:36,825
<font color="#ffff00">No. Tell me.</font>

927
00:59:38,905 --> 00:59:40,025
<font color="#00ffff">God is real.</font>

928
00:59:41,665 --> 00:59:45,105
<font color="#00ffff">God is real, and I've found him at</font>
<font color="#00ffff">last.</font>

929
00:59:46,745 --> 00:59:49,823
<font color="#ffff00">You have found the Devil.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">If it takes the Devil</font>

930
00:59:49,825 --> 00:59:52,543
<font color="#00ffff">to bring me to my Lord, then I say,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">"Bring on the Devil!"</font>

931
00:59:52,545 --> 00:59:54,463
<font color="#ffffff">SCOFFS</font>

932
00:59:54,465 --> 00:59:55,983
<font color="#ffff00">I don't!</font>

933
00:59:55,985 --> 00:59:57,343
<font color="#00ffff">And why not?</font>

934
00:59:57,345 --> 01:00:00,423
<font color="#00ffff">God saved you for a reason,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">don't you think?</font>

935
01:00:00,425 --> 01:00:01,785
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not saved!</font>

936
01:00:04,305 --> 01:00:06,143
<font color="#ffff00">I'm nothing.</font>

937
01:00:06,145 --> 01:00:08,463
<font color="#00ffff">Would Mina think that?</font>

938
01:00:08,465 --> 01:00:10,905
<font color="#ffff00">If she could see me, yes, she would.</font>

939
01:00:14,225 --> 01:00:15,305
<font color="#ffff00">Look at me.</font>

940
01:00:18,385 --> 01:00:20,663
<font color="#ffff00">I can't even remember her face.</font>

941
01:00:20,665 --> 01:00:24,065
<font color="#00ffff">Yes. I think you have proven that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to our satisfaction.</font>

942
01:00:27,145 --> 01:00:28,465
<font color="#ffffff">SISTER ANGELA WEEPS</font>

943
01:00:29,745 --> 01:00:32,983
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Harker, I apologise for the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">deception.</font>

944
01:00:32,985 --> 01:00:36,105
<font color="#00ffff">It was necessary she heard the story</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from your own lips.</font>

945
01:00:51,465 --> 01:00:55,305
<font color="#00ff00">You may have forgotten</font>
<font color="#00ff00">your fiancee's face...</font>

946
01:01:00,305 --> 01:01:02,225
<font color="#00ff00">..but I have not lost you yet.</font>

947
01:01:07,265 --> 01:01:08,745
<font color="#00ff00">Hello, Johnny.</font>

948
01:01:10,545 --> 01:01:13,743
<font color="#00ff00">Your eyes are still blue, at least.</font>

949
01:01:13,745 --> 01:01:18,023
<font color="#00ffff">Having established your identity, it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">was not difficult to trace you back</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to England</font>

950
01:01:18,025 --> 01:01:20,023
<font color="#00ffff">and find your worried fiancee.</font>

951
01:01:20,025 --> 01:01:22,025
<font color="#00ffff">I have a detective acquaintance in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">London.</font>

952
01:01:26,625 --> 01:01:28,023
<font color="#ffff00">Mina?</font>

953
01:01:28,025 --> 01:01:32,305
<font color="#00ff00">Did you really think,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">even in your darkest moment...</font>

954
01:01:33,665 --> 01:01:35,583
<font color="#00ff00">..that I wouldn't come for you?</font>

955
01:01:35,585 --> 01:01:41,145
<font color="#00ff00">Did you think it was even possible</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that I could abandon the man I love?</font>

956
01:01:43,665 --> 01:01:45,865
<font color="#ffff00">I am no longer that man.</font>

957
01:01:47,545 --> 01:01:48,825
<font color="#00ff00">Dearest one.</font>

958
01:01:50,705 --> 01:01:52,065
<font color="#00ff00">We are to be married.</font>

959
01:01:53,265 --> 01:01:54,945
<font color="#00ff00">So let me be plain.</font>

960
01:01:56,025 --> 01:02:00,063
<font color="#00ff00">Who you are will always be my</font>
<font color="#00ff00">decision. Yes...</font>

961
01:02:00,065 --> 01:02:01,263
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMS</font>

962
01:02:01,265 --> 01:02:02,783
<font color="#ffffff">BATS SCREECH</font>

963
01:02:02,785 --> 01:02:05,223
<font color="#ffffff">WOMEN SCREAM</font>

964
01:02:05,225 --> 01:02:07,305
<font color="#ffff00">Dracula is here!</font>

965
01:02:09,265 --> 01:02:11,103
<font color="#00ffff">How exciting!</font>

966
01:02:11,105 --> 01:02:13,505
<font color="#ffffff">BATS SCREECH</font>

967
01:02:19,185 --> 01:02:20,983
<font color="#00ffff">Look after Mina.</font>

968
01:02:20,985 --> 01:02:22,543
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES</font>

969
01:02:22,545 --> 01:02:24,145
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMING IN THE DISTANCE</font>

970
01:02:40,185 --> 01:02:43,025
<font color="#ffffff">WOLF HOWLS</font>

971
01:02:52,185 --> 01:02:53,505
<font color="#ffff00">Mina?</font>

972
01:02:54,545 --> 01:02:56,065
<font color="#ffff00">Take it, please.</font>

973
01:02:57,265 --> 01:02:58,663
<font color="#00ff00">Why?</font>

974
01:02:58,665 --> 01:03:01,423
<font color="#ffff00">Because you're bleeding.</font>

975
01:03:01,425 --> 01:03:03,465
<font color="#ffff00">And I can't stand it.</font>

976
01:03:06,385 --> 01:03:07,903
<font color="#ffffff">SHOUTS: </font><font color="#ffff00">Take it!</font>

977
01:03:07,905 --> 01:03:09,385
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

978
01:03:16,745 --> 01:03:19,305
<font color="#ffffff">WOLF HOWLS</font>

979
01:03:22,065 --> 01:03:23,983
<font color="#00ffff">Mother Superior, on no account</font>

980
01:03:23,985 --> 01:03:25,303
<font color="#00ffff">invite that creature in.</font>

981
01:03:25,305 --> 01:03:26,423
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLING</font>

982
01:03:26,425 --> 01:03:29,663
<font color="#00ff00">That is not a temptation</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with which I was struggling.</font>

983
01:03:29,665 --> 01:03:32,105
<font color="#00ff00">What is happening? What is this?</font>

984
01:03:33,265 --> 01:03:36,423
<font color="#00ffff">We are under attack</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from the forces of darkness.</font>

985
01:03:36,425 --> 01:03:39,943
<font color="#00ff00">Why would the forces of darkness</font>
<font color="#00ff00">wish to attack a convent?</font>

986
01:03:39,945 --> 01:03:41,743
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps they are sensitive to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">criticism.</font>

987
01:03:41,745 --> 01:03:43,145
<font color="#ffffff">LOW SNARL</font>

988
01:03:46,065 --> 01:03:48,225
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

989
01:03:49,465 --> 01:03:51,223
<font color="#00ffff">I know who you are.</font>

990
01:03:51,225 --> 01:03:56,585
<font color="#00ffff">I've studied the legends. I am fully</font>
<font color="#00ffff">aware that I am addressing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Count Dracula.</font>

991
01:04:00,305 --> 01:04:03,263
<font color="#00ffff">The bats are a little noisy.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Would you mind?</font>

992
01:04:03,265 --> 01:04:05,025
<font color="#ffffff">HOWLS</font>

993
01:04:07,625 --> 01:04:10,265
<font color="#ffffff">SCREECHING FADES</font>

994
01:04:16,865 --> 01:04:18,583
<font color="#00ff00">Listen to me.</font>

995
01:04:18,585 --> 01:04:21,905
<font color="#00ff00">You are Jonathan Harker.</font>

996
01:04:23,025 --> 01:04:25,583
<font color="#00ff00">You would never harm me.</font>

997
01:04:25,585 --> 01:04:27,303
<font color="#ffffff">STAKE CLATTERS</font>

998
01:04:27,305 --> 01:04:31,585
<font color="#ffff00">I know I am safe with you.</font>

999
01:04:43,785 --> 01:04:45,785
<font color="#ffffff">SOBS: </font><font color="#00ff00">It's me.</font>

1000
01:04:49,025 --> 01:04:50,225
<font color="#00ff00">Look at me.</font>

1001
01:04:51,665 --> 01:04:52,745
<font color="#00ff00">See me.</font>

1002
01:04:53,825 --> 01:04:56,185
<font color="#00ff00">My blue-eyed Johnny.</font>

1003
01:05:04,985 --> 01:05:06,785
<font color="#00ff00">No, Johnny...</font>

1004
01:05:07,985 --> 01:05:09,265
<font color="#00ff00">Don't.</font>

1005
01:05:10,625 --> 01:05:12,943
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, please, don't.</font>

1006
01:05:12,945 --> 01:05:14,745
<font color="#00ff00">You don't need to do that.</font>

1007
01:05:15,825 --> 01:05:17,463
<font color="#00ff00">I know you don't.</font>

1008
01:05:17,465 --> 01:05:19,583
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMS: </font><font color="#00ff00">Johnny!</font>

1009
01:05:19,585 --> 01:05:21,383
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1010
01:05:21,385 --> 01:05:25,143
<font color="#00ffff">The sun is down.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You don't need to hide any more.</font>

1011
01:05:25,145 --> 01:05:27,905
<font color="#00ffff">Or are you too afraid</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to step from the shadows?</font>

1012
01:05:30,065 --> 01:05:31,623
<font color="#ffffff">BARKS</font>

1013
01:05:31,625 --> 01:05:34,665
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1014
01:05:47,025 --> 01:05:49,305
<font color="#ffffff">GURGLING</font>

1015
01:05:55,425 --> 01:05:57,465
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

1016
01:06:21,585 --> 01:06:23,703
<font color="#ffff00">Let me...</font>

1017
01:06:23,705 --> 01:06:26,343
<font color="#00ff00">Johnny...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Let me.</font>

1018
01:06:26,345 --> 01:06:28,543
<font color="#ffff00">Please...</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Johnny!</font>

1019
01:06:28,545 --> 01:06:30,345
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

1020
01:06:33,705 --> 01:06:36,105
<font color="#ffffff">MINA SCREAMS</font>

1021
01:06:56,185 --> 01:06:57,625
<font color="#00ff00">No...</font>

1022
01:07:02,265 --> 01:07:04,105
<font color="#00ff00">I'm sorry.</font>

1023
01:07:07,945 --> 01:07:09,943
<font color="#00ff00">Somebody help!</font>

1024
01:07:09,945 --> 01:07:11,185
<font color="#00ff00">Please!</font>

1025
01:07:18,705 --> 01:07:19,743
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMS</font>

1026
01:07:19,745 --> 01:07:21,223
<font color="#ffffff">BONES CRUNCH</font>

1027
01:07:21,225 --> 01:07:22,903
<font color="#ffffff">WHIMPERS</font>

1028
01:07:22,905 --> 01:07:24,985
<font color="#00ff00">This is devilry.</font>

1029
01:07:26,025 --> 01:07:27,505
<font color="#00ffff">It's worse than that.</font>

1030
01:07:28,745 --> 01:07:30,223
<font color="#00ffff">It is the Devil.</font>

1031
01:07:30,225 --> 01:07:32,145
<font color="#ffffff">GRUNTS</font>

1032
01:07:34,185 --> 01:07:36,385
<font color="#ffffff">MOTHER SUPERIOR GASPS</font>

1033
01:07:54,585 --> 01:07:56,425
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know about you girls...</font>

1034
01:07:57,665 --> 01:08:00,145
<font color="#ffffff">...but I do love a bit of fur.</font>

1035
01:08:01,225 --> 01:08:03,785
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

1036
01:08:09,385 --> 01:08:11,865
<font color="#ffffff">Suffer unto me.</font>

1037
01:08:14,905 --> 01:08:16,623
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHS</font>

1038
01:08:16,625 --> 01:08:18,503
<font color="#ffffff">BELL RINGS OUT</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not sure</font>

1039
01:08:18,505 --> 01:08:22,263
<font color="#ffffff">what legends you've been reading,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">but bells don't have any effect on</font>
<font color="#ffffff">me.</font>

1040
01:08:22,265 --> 01:08:24,383
<font color="#00ffff">This one will.</font>

1041
01:08:24,385 --> 01:08:25,823
<font color="#ffffff">Ooh!</font>

1042
01:08:25,825 --> 01:08:29,143
<font color="#00ff00">Sister Agatha, have you been up</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to one of your secret projects</font>
<font color="#00ff00">again?</font>

1043
01:08:29,145 --> 01:08:31,783
<font color="#00ffff">You'd better hope so.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">This is exciting.</font>

1044
01:08:31,785 --> 01:08:35,983
<font color="#ffffff">This'll be the most nuns I've had</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in one sitting.</font>

1045
01:08:35,985 --> 01:08:37,903
<font color="#00ffff">Sisters, present arms.</font>

1046
01:08:37,905 --> 01:08:39,823
<font color="#ffffff">DRACULA: Ooh!</font>

1047
01:08:39,825 --> 01:08:43,543
<font color="#ffffff">I see my arrival was anticipated.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I was aware of the possibility.</font>

1048
01:08:43,545 --> 01:08:45,623
<font color="#00ff00">Sister Agatha, what have you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">brought down upon us?</font>

1049
01:08:45,625 --> 01:08:46,663
<font color="#ffffff">Cooee!</font>

1050
01:08:46,665 --> 01:08:47,823
<font color="#ffffff">MOTHER SUPERIOR GASPS</font>

1051
01:08:47,825 --> 01:08:49,143
<font color="#ffffff">Hello!</font>

1052
01:08:49,145 --> 01:08:50,905
<font color="#ffffff">Hello, ladies.</font>

1053
01:08:53,025 --> 01:08:55,143
<font color="#ffffff">I don't want to worry you,</font>

1054
01:08:55,145 --> 01:08:57,783
<font color="#ffffff">but the army of the faithful</font>
<font color="#ffffff">can't seem to look me in the eye.</font>

1055
01:08:57,785 --> 01:08:59,263
<font color="#00ffff">You're naked, and they're nuns.</font>

1056
01:08:59,265 --> 01:09:01,063
<font color="#00ffff">It isn't your eye they're not</font>
<font color="#00ffff">looking at.</font>

1057
01:09:01,065 --> 01:09:03,343
<font color="#ffffff">Well, isn't anyone going to invite</font>
<font color="#ffffff">me in?</font>

1058
01:09:03,345 --> 01:09:07,783
<font color="#ffffff">I've come a long way to see you.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Certainly not.</font>

1059
01:09:07,785 --> 01:09:08,943
<font color="#00ffff">Sister Rosa, the key!</font>

1060
01:09:08,945 --> 01:09:11,143
<font color="#ffffff">MOTHER SUPERIOR:</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You can't be serious.</font>

1061
01:09:11,145 --> 01:09:13,383
<font color="#00ffff">I'm more than serious.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I'm completely confident.</font>

1062
01:09:13,385 --> 01:09:15,223
<font color="#ffffff">How did you know that I was coming?</font>

1063
01:09:15,225 --> 01:09:18,463
<font color="#00ffff">There's a man here you consider</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to be your property.</font>

1064
01:09:18,465 --> 01:09:21,743
<font color="#ffffff">My bride.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">He's what drew you here, I think.</font>

1065
01:09:21,745 --> 01:09:24,903
<font color="#ffffff">A bee can always find nectar.</font>

1066
01:09:24,905 --> 01:09:26,863
<font color="#00ffff">And a trap always needs honey.</font>

1067
01:09:26,865 --> 01:09:28,263
<font color="#ffffff">I don't think this is a trap.</font>

1068
01:09:28,265 --> 01:09:31,545
<font color="#00ffff">Well, it wouldn't be a very good</font>
<font color="#00ffff">trap if you did.</font>

1069
01:09:33,425 --> 01:09:35,585
<font color="#00ffff">Thank you, Sister.</font>

1070
01:09:37,785 --> 01:09:39,463
<font color="#ffffff">BREATHES RASPINGLY</font>

1071
01:09:39,465 --> 01:09:42,945
<font color="#00ffff">Count Dracula,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">please attend my words with care.</font>

1072
01:09:46,185 --> 01:09:47,865
<font color="#ffffff">CHAINS CLANG</font>

1073
01:09:49,465 --> 01:09:52,903
<font color="#00ffff">This is St Mary's Convent of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Budapest,</font>

1074
01:09:52,905 --> 01:09:55,183
<font color="#00ffff">and you are not welcome here.</font>

1075
01:09:55,185 --> 01:09:59,103
<font color="#00ffff">You are most specifically not</font>
<font color="#00ffff">invited in.</font>

1076
01:09:59,105 --> 01:10:01,903
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS AND HISSES</font>

1077
01:10:01,905 --> 01:10:04,545
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1078
01:10:06,225 --> 01:10:07,503
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1079
01:10:07,505 --> 01:10:09,025
<font color="#ffffff">SISTER AGATHA: </font><font color="#00ffff">Oh!</font>

1080
01:10:10,705 --> 01:10:12,183
<font color="#00ffff">So it's true, then.</font>

1081
01:10:12,185 --> 01:10:14,423
<font color="#00ffff">That's interesting.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">MOTHER SUPERIOR: </font><font color="#00ff00">What is?</font>

1082
01:10:14,425 --> 01:10:18,103
<font color="#00ffff">A vampire may not enter any abode</font>
<font color="#00ffff">unless invited in.</font>

1083
01:10:18,105 --> 01:10:20,463
<font color="#00ffff">I wasn't sure about that one.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">A vampire?</font>

1084
01:10:20,465 --> 01:10:22,423
<font color="#ffffff">You unlocked the gate</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and you weren't sure?</font>

1085
01:10:22,425 --> 01:10:24,103
<font color="#00ff00">A vampire?!</font>

1086
01:10:24,105 --> 01:10:27,303
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, the iron wasn't keeping you out.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You could have torn it apart like</font>
<font color="#00ffff">matchwood.</font>

1087
01:10:27,305 --> 01:10:28,903
<font color="#ffffff">I could tear you apart.</font>

1088
01:10:28,905 --> 01:10:31,343
<font color="#00ffff">Not from out there, you couldn't.</font>

1089
01:10:31,345 --> 01:10:33,703
<font color="#00ffff">But what's stopping you?</font>

1090
01:10:33,705 --> 01:10:35,703
<font color="#00ffff">A-a feeling?</font>

1091
01:10:35,705 --> 01:10:36,823
<font color="#00ffff">A force?</font>

1092
01:10:36,825 --> 01:10:40,303
<font color="#00ffff">Is it physical or mental?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Why do you need an invitation?</font>

1093
01:10:40,305 --> 01:10:43,783
<font color="#ffffff">Do you expect me to tell you?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, I don't even expect you to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">know.</font>

1094
01:10:43,785 --> 01:10:46,863
<font color="#00ffff">A beast can follow rules. I don't</font>
<font color="#00ffff">expect it to understand them.</font>

1095
01:10:46,865 --> 01:10:48,665
<font color="#ffffff">NUNS GASP</font>

1096
01:10:50,225 --> 01:10:52,345
<font color="#ffffff">I am more than a beast.</font>

1097
01:10:53,385 --> 01:10:54,943
<font color="#00ffff">In what way?</font>

1098
01:10:54,945 --> 01:10:58,223
<font color="#00ffff">By your own account, you've been</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on this Earth for hundreds of years,</font>

1099
01:10:58,225 --> 01:11:00,863
<font color="#00ffff">and you can't even walk into a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">nunnery?</font>

1100
01:11:00,865 --> 01:11:02,383
<font color="#00ffff">An ox could do it.</font>

1101
01:11:02,385 --> 01:11:05,543
<font color="#00ffff">How are you more than a beast?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Do you want me to show you?</font>

1102
01:11:05,545 --> 01:11:06,703
<font color="#00ffff">Of course.</font>

1103
01:11:06,705 --> 01:11:08,063
<font color="#00ffff">I'm waiting.</font>

1104
01:11:08,065 --> 01:11:10,383
<font color="#ffffff">WHISPERS: Come here. Come here.</font>

1105
01:11:10,385 --> 01:11:12,183
<font color="#ffffff">Come here. Come here a moment.</font>

1106
01:11:12,185 --> 01:11:14,505
<font color="#ffffff">Come closer.</font>

1107
01:11:16,065 --> 01:11:17,703
<font color="#ffffff">Look at them.</font>

1108
01:11:17,705 --> 01:11:19,823
<font color="#ffffff">Look at your sisters.</font>

1109
01:11:19,825 --> 01:11:21,703
<font color="#00ffff">Armed and ready.</font>

1110
01:11:21,705 --> 01:11:23,905
<font color="#ffffff">You're not looking.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I don't need to.</font>

1111
01:11:26,785 --> 01:11:29,583
<font color="#ffffff">One of them - that's all I need.</font>

1112
01:11:29,585 --> 01:11:33,145
<font color="#ffffff">If just one of your pretty little</font>
<font color="#ffffff">army beckons me in...</font>

1113
01:11:34,945 --> 01:11:39,943
<font color="#ffffff">..I will tear your world to pieces</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and I will drink my fill.</font>

1114
01:11:39,945 --> 01:11:42,063
<font color="#00ffff">Why would they invite you in?</font>

1115
01:11:42,065 --> 01:11:43,143
<font color="#00ffff">What do you have to offer?</font>

1116
01:11:43,145 --> 01:11:45,063
<font color="#ffffff">Eternal life.</font>

1117
01:11:45,065 --> 01:11:47,383
<font color="#00ffff">Well, they have that already.</font>

1118
01:11:47,385 --> 01:11:48,623
<font color="#00ffff">Thanks.</font>

1119
01:11:48,625 --> 01:11:51,343
<font color="#ffffff">Starting tonight, because the first</font>

1120
01:11:51,345 --> 01:11:53,903
<font color="#ffffff">one to invite me in stays at my</font>
<font color="#ffffff">side.</font>

1121
01:11:53,905 --> 01:11:56,263
<font color="#ffffff">The others I will tear apart,</font>

1122
01:11:56,265 --> 01:11:58,903
<font color="#ffffff">and, ladies...</font>

1123
01:11:58,905 --> 01:12:02,543
<font color="#ffffff">..I will take my time.</font>

1124
01:12:02,545 --> 01:12:04,823
<font color="#ffffff">One should never rush a nun.</font>

1125
01:12:04,825 --> 01:12:07,463
<font color="#00ff00">Your words are not welcome here.</font>

1126
01:12:07,465 --> 01:12:11,383
<font color="#ffffff">Well, if you find you're not tempted</font>
<font color="#ffffff">by my offer,</font>

1127
01:12:11,385 --> 01:12:13,585
<font color="#ffffff">ask yourself this.</font>

1128
01:12:14,785 --> 01:12:16,225
<font color="#ffffff">Who is?</font>

1129
01:12:17,385 --> 01:12:19,183
<font color="#ffffff">Who's weakest?</font>

1130
01:12:19,185 --> 01:12:20,703
<font color="#ffffff">Who's the most afraid?</font>

1131
01:12:20,705 --> 01:12:22,463
<font color="#ffffff">Who will break first?</font>

1132
01:12:22,465 --> 01:12:26,025
<font color="#ffffff">And is there still time for it to be</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you?</font>

1133
01:12:27,385 --> 01:12:28,663
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHS: What's that?</font>

1134
01:12:28,665 --> 01:12:33,103
<font color="#ffffff">What are you doing?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You wanted to know who's weakest?</font>

1135
01:12:33,105 --> 01:12:34,503
<font color="#00ffff">I'm showing you.</font>

1136
01:12:34,505 --> 01:12:36,825
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1137
01:12:44,985 --> 01:12:47,665
<font color="#ffffff">ROARS</font>

1138
01:12:52,385 --> 01:12:54,623
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, go on, help yourself!</font>

1139
01:12:54,625 --> 01:12:56,543
<font color="#00ffff">There's a dog comes past here most</font>
<font color="#00ffff">days.</font>

1140
01:12:56,545 --> 01:12:58,823
<font color="#00ffff">We often give it scraps.</font>

1141
01:12:58,825 --> 01:13:00,343
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1142
01:13:00,345 --> 01:13:03,983
<font color="#00ffff">Go on. You've come so far.</font>

1143
01:13:03,985 --> 01:13:06,065
<font color="#00ffff">I'm sure you could do with a drink.</font>

1144
01:13:09,585 --> 01:13:11,663
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1145
01:13:11,665 --> 01:13:15,543
<font color="#00ffff">Hmm. You see,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I'm not certain I see the appeal.</font>

1146
01:13:15,545 --> 01:13:16,983
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1147
01:13:16,985 --> 01:13:18,183
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1148
01:13:18,185 --> 01:13:21,143
<font color="#00ffff">Each to his own, I suppose.</font>

1149
01:13:21,145 --> 01:13:23,265
<font color="#ffffff">Do you think...</font>

1150
01:13:24,505 --> 01:13:27,503
<font color="#ffffff">...provoking me is clever?</font>

1151
01:13:27,505 --> 01:13:29,505
<font color="#00ffff">Yes. I do.</font>

1152
01:13:31,625 --> 01:13:33,943
<font color="#00ffff">I want to learn about you.</font>

1153
01:13:33,945 --> 01:13:36,185
<font color="#00ffff">I want to see the limit</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of your capability.</font>

1154
01:13:37,425 --> 01:13:40,343
<font color="#00ffff">That's the point of this experiment.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You have no conception.</font>

1155
01:13:40,345 --> 01:13:42,145
<font color="#ffffff">Not the first idea.</font>

1156
01:13:45,065 --> 01:13:47,425
<font color="#ffffff">Hmm...</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Here, boy!</font>

1157
01:13:52,185 --> 01:13:54,063
<font color="#00ff00">This is contemptible.</font>

1158
01:13:54,065 --> 01:13:57,263
<font color="#00ff00">You are without shame.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Be careful...</font>

1159
01:13:57,265 --> 01:13:58,663
<font color="#ffffff">..what you say to me.</font>

1160
01:13:58,665 --> 01:14:01,743
<font color="#00ffff">Don't speak with your mouth full.</font>

1161
01:14:01,745 --> 01:14:04,623
<font color="#00ffff">She's earned the right to express</font>
<font color="#00ffff">her contempt, you know. We all have.</font>

1162
01:14:04,625 --> 01:14:09,703
<font color="#00ffff">Each of these women in front of you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">has turned her back on earthly</font>
<font color="#00ffff">pleasures.</font>

1163
01:14:09,705 --> 01:14:12,543
<font color="#00ffff">Resisting all forms of temptation,</font>

1164
01:14:12,545 --> 01:14:16,383
<font color="#00ffff">we have freed ourselves of appetite</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and therefore of fear.</font>

1165
01:14:16,385 --> 01:14:20,145
<font color="#00ffff">That is why you can't bear</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the sight of this.</font>

1166
01:14:21,225 --> 01:14:24,903
<font color="#00ffff">It speaks of a holy virtue</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you do not possess.</font>

1167
01:14:24,905 --> 01:14:27,103
<font color="#00ffff">It is goodness incarnate.</font>

1168
01:14:27,105 --> 01:14:29,225
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHS SOFTLY</font>

1169
01:14:31,705 --> 01:14:34,985
<font color="#ffffff">For a moment there,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I thought you were clever.</font>

1170
01:14:36,585 --> 01:14:38,103
<font color="#ffffff">But no.</font>

1171
01:14:38,105 --> 01:14:41,103
<font color="#ffffff">No, that's not why I fear the cross.</font>

1172
01:14:41,105 --> 01:14:43,223
<font color="#ffffff">Goodness has got nothing to do with</font>
<font color="#ffffff">it.</font>

1173
01:14:43,225 --> 01:14:48,143
<font color="#00ffff">So you say, but how can a mere beast</font>
<font color="#00ffff">understand its own fear?</font>

1174
01:14:48,145 --> 01:14:51,383
<font color="#00ffff">No-one will invite you in,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Count Dracula.</font>

1175
01:14:51,385 --> 01:14:53,703
<font color="#00ffff">They'll just pity you right where</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you are.</font>

1176
01:14:53,705 --> 01:14:55,983
<font color="#ffffff">Who are you?</font>

1177
01:14:55,985 --> 01:14:59,623
<font color="#00ffff">Finish your scraps. That's all</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you'll be getting tonight.</font>

1178
01:14:59,625 --> 01:15:00,865
<font color="#ffffff">Agatha...</font>

1179
01:15:01,905 --> 01:15:04,303
<font color="#ffffff">..that's the name, isn't it?</font>

1180
01:15:04,305 --> 01:15:08,183
<font color="#00ffff">Mother Superior used my name. You</font>
<font color="#00ffff">heard her. You'll have to do better</font>
<font color="#00ffff">than that.</font>

1181
01:15:08,185 --> 01:15:11,785
<font color="#ffffff">You're from somewhere else, I think.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Um...</font>

1182
01:15:14,545 --> 01:15:16,263
<font color="#ffffff">Holland, right?</font>

1183
01:15:16,265 --> 01:15:19,585
<font color="#00ffff">Well, you can tell as much from my</font>
<font color="#00ffff">accent, I think. I bid you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">goodnight.</font>

1184
01:15:23,945 --> 01:15:25,785
<font color="#ffffff">Helsing!</font>

1185
01:15:26,825 --> 01:15:29,265
<font color="#ffffff">Van Helsing!</font>

1186
01:15:30,545 --> 01:15:36,503
<font color="#ffffff">What is your interest in me,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Agatha Van Helsing?</font>

1187
01:15:36,505 --> 01:15:38,943
<font color="#ffffff">Who are you?</font>

1188
01:15:38,945 --> 01:15:42,063
<font color="#00ffff">Your every nightmare at once.</font>

1189
01:15:42,065 --> 01:15:44,705
<font color="#00ffff">An educated woman in a crucifix.</font>

1190
01:15:46,785 --> 01:15:48,505
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS SOFTLY</font>

1191
01:15:50,305 --> 01:15:52,623
<font color="#ffffff">KNIFE CLATTERS</font>

1192
01:15:52,625 --> 01:15:53,663
<font color="#ffffff">ROARS</font>

1193
01:15:53,665 --> 01:15:55,105
<font color="#ffffff">NUNS SHRIEK</font>

1194
01:16:00,065 --> 01:16:01,985
<font color="#ffffff">SNARLS</font>

1195
01:16:19,625 --> 01:16:21,105
<font color="#00ffff">He was a brave man.</font>

1196
01:16:22,425 --> 01:16:24,983
<font color="#00ffff">He must have loved you very much.</font>

1197
01:16:24,985 --> 01:16:26,505
<font color="#00ff00">What is he?</font>

1198
01:16:27,825 --> 01:16:29,545
<font color="#00ff00">What is Count Dracula?</font>

1199
01:16:33,625 --> 01:16:37,305
<font color="#00ffff">In life, he was a prince of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">exceptional learning and attainment.</font>

1200
01:16:38,425 --> 01:16:41,623
<font color="#00ffff">In death, I suppose you could say</font>
<font color="#00ffff">he's the best of the vampires.</font>

1201
01:16:41,625 --> 01:16:44,383
<font color="#00ff00">The best?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">The most successful, I mean.</font>

1202
01:16:44,385 --> 01:16:48,543
<font color="#00ffff">Most are feral, half-mad. They</font>
<font color="#00ffff">rarely last long and yet, somehow,</font>

1203
01:16:48,545 --> 01:16:51,503
<font color="#00ffff">Dracula has found a way to retain</font>
<font color="#00ffff">his human form and intellect,</font>

1204
01:16:51,505 --> 01:16:54,423
<font color="#00ffff">more or less intact,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for hundreds of years.</font>

1205
01:16:54,425 --> 01:16:55,823
<font color="#00ff00">By drinking blood?</font>

1206
01:16:55,825 --> 01:16:57,463
<font color="#00ffff">Ah, they all drink blood.</font>

1207
01:16:57,465 --> 01:16:59,663
<font color="#00ffff">Dracula has learned to do it well...</font>

1208
01:16:59,665 --> 01:17:02,145
<font color="#00ffff">..I think by choosing his victims</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the greatest of care.</font>

1209
01:17:03,745 --> 01:17:08,105
<font color="#00ffff">Even in death, he has retained</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the discrimination of an aristocrat.</font>

1210
01:17:11,665 --> 01:17:13,785
<font color="#00ff00">And so he took my Johnny.</font>

1211
01:17:17,225 --> 01:17:21,105
<font color="#ffffff">SISTER AGATHA: </font><font color="#00ffff">Come, the Mother</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Superior will want to lead us in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">prayer.</font>

1212
01:17:22,465 --> 01:17:25,303
<font color="#ffffff">MINA: </font><font color="#00ff00">I don't see the point in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">praying.</font>

1213
01:17:25,305 --> 01:17:26,905
<font color="#00ff00">God is nowhere.</font>

1214
01:17:28,425 --> 01:17:32,745
<font color="#00ffff">In which case, it is up to us to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">stop Count Dracula.</font>

1215
01:17:36,985 --> 01:17:38,463
<font color="#00ff00">And we will.</font>

1216
01:17:38,465 --> 01:17:39,703
<font color="#00ff00">Won't we?</font>

1217
01:17:39,705 --> 01:17:41,023
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

1218
01:17:41,025 --> 01:17:42,065
<font color="#00ffff">We will.</font>

1219
01:17:44,585 --> 01:17:47,463
<font color="#00ff00">Goodbye, Johnny Blue Eyes.</font>

1220
01:17:47,465 --> 01:17:49,785
<font color="#00ff00">I shan't ever love anyone else, you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">know.</font>

1221
01:17:51,865 --> 01:17:53,265
<font color="#00ffff">Quite right.</font>

1222
01:17:55,905 --> 01:17:58,425
<font color="#ffffff">LOW GROWLING</font>

1223
01:18:02,505 --> 01:18:04,705
<font color="#ffffff">SWORD CLATTERS</font>

1224
01:18:21,545 --> 01:18:23,985
<font color="#ffffff">WIND WHISTLES</font>

1225
01:18:25,065 --> 01:18:26,663
<font color="#ffffff">WHISPERS: Johnny.</font>

1226
01:18:26,665 --> 01:18:29,225
<font color="#ffffff">Johnny Blue Eyes.</font>

1227
01:18:31,105 --> 01:18:32,543
<font color="#ffffff">Suicide doesn't work.</font>

1228
01:18:32,545 --> 01:18:34,783
<font color="#ffffff">Don't you think the undead</font>
<font color="#ffffff">have tried that?</font>

1229
01:18:34,785 --> 01:18:36,143
<font color="#ffffff">HARKER WHEEZES</font>

1230
01:18:36,145 --> 01:18:38,823
<font color="#ffffff">Stake through the heart, that's</font>
<font color="#ffffff">fine,</font>

1231
01:18:38,825 --> 01:18:40,905
<font color="#ffffff">but someone else needs to put it</font>
<font color="#ffffff">there.</font>

1232
01:18:42,585 --> 01:18:44,745
<font color="#ffffff">I'm willing to give it a try.</font>

1233
01:18:45,865 --> 01:18:48,423
<font color="#ffffff">Do you want me to do that?</font>

1234
01:18:48,425 --> 01:18:50,623
<font color="#ffffff">Do you want me to kill you properly?</font>

1235
01:18:50,625 --> 01:18:52,543
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS</font>

1236
01:18:52,545 --> 01:18:54,065
<font color="#ffffff">All you have to do...</font>

1237
01:18:57,065 --> 01:18:58,665
<font color="#ffffff">...is invite me in.</font>

1238
01:19:03,905 --> 01:19:08,103
<font color="#ffffff">MOTHER SUPERIOR: </font><font color="#ffff00">We face danger,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">we face evil, which stands at the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">gate</font>

1239
01:19:08,105 --> 01:19:10,983
<font color="#ffff00">of our most holy sanctuary.</font>

1240
01:19:10,985 --> 01:19:14,063
<font color="#ffff00">God is with us, as we know.</font>

1241
01:19:14,065 --> 01:19:15,225
<font color="#ffff00">God's love is eternal.</font>

1242
01:19:16,505 --> 01:19:17,825
<font color="#ffff00">This we know too.</font>

1243
01:19:19,185 --> 01:19:22,225
<font color="#ffff00">Tonight, in our most deadly hour...</font>

1244
01:19:23,425 --> 01:19:26,383
<font color="#ffff00">...do we think our God will remember</font>
<font color="#ffff00">us?</font>

1245
01:19:26,385 --> 01:19:30,505
<font color="#ffff00">Will he reach down</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and save us from death's shadow?</font>

1246
01:19:32,625 --> 01:19:33,745
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

1247
01:19:34,785 --> 01:19:36,065
<font color="#ffff00">No, he will not.</font>

1248
01:19:37,705 --> 01:19:41,383
<font color="#ffff00">Where in our world is God to be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">found?</font>

1249
01:19:41,385 --> 01:19:43,183
<font color="#ffff00">In our prayer?</font>

1250
01:19:43,185 --> 01:19:44,983
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

1251
01:19:44,985 --> 01:19:46,463
<font color="#ffff00">In our song?</font>

1252
01:19:46,465 --> 01:19:48,063
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

1253
01:19:48,065 --> 01:19:50,943
<font color="#ffff00">In our suffering, in our endurance?</font>

1254
01:19:50,945 --> 01:19:52,983
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

1255
01:19:52,985 --> 01:19:55,063
<font color="#ffff00">Faith is not a transaction.</font>

1256
01:19:55,065 --> 01:19:57,983
<font color="#ffff00">You do not barter with the infinite.</font>

1257
01:19:57,985 --> 01:19:59,625
<font color="#ffff00">You align with it.</font>

1258
01:20:02,265 --> 01:20:04,745
<font color="#ffff00">So, then, where do we find our God?</font>

1259
01:20:06,465 --> 01:20:08,983
<font color="#ffff00">Sisters, I will tell you.</font>

1260
01:20:08,985 --> 01:20:12,463
<font color="#ffff00">When you stand in the deepest pit,</font>

1261
01:20:12,465 --> 01:20:16,143
<font color="#ffff00">alone, without hope or help,</font>

1262
01:20:16,145 --> 01:20:19,423
<font color="#ffff00">and yet still know right from</font>
<font color="#ffff00">wrong...</font>

1263
01:20:19,425 --> 01:20:22,265
<font color="#ffff00">When there is only darkness and</font>
<font color="#ffff00">despair...</font>

1264
01:20:23,345 --> 01:20:26,383
<font color="#ffff00">..and yet you feel humming in your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">blood,</font>

1265
01:20:26,385 --> 01:20:28,465
<font color="#ffff00">the difference between good and</font>
<font color="#ffff00">bad...</font>

1266
01:20:29,545 --> 01:20:32,585
<font color="#ffff00">When you are beyond rescue or reward</font>
<font color="#ffff00">or judgment...</font>

1267
01:20:33,985 --> 01:20:38,983
<font color="#ffff00">..and you still look evil in the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">face and say, "No!</font>

1268
01:20:38,985 --> 01:20:42,345
<font color="#ffff00">"This far but no further.</font>

1269
01:20:43,585 --> 01:20:44,945
<font color="#ffff00">"No!"</font>

1270
01:20:48,385 --> 01:20:53,183
<font color="#ffff00">Whose voice is that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">who is with you in that darkness?</font>

1271
01:20:53,185 --> 01:20:56,585
<font color="#ffff00">Whose voice keeps you to the path?</font>

1272
01:20:58,705 --> 01:21:03,263
<font color="#ffff00">Darkness and evil</font>
<font color="#ffff00">may seem compelling to us all,</font>

1273
01:21:03,265 --> 01:21:07,183
<font color="#ffff00">and I believe it is because,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in their presence,</font>

1274
01:21:07,185 --> 01:21:10,185
<font color="#ffff00">we can feel God in our hearts.</font>

1275
01:21:11,625 --> 01:21:15,265
<font color="#ffff00">No, he will not reach down to save</font>
<font color="#ffff00">us.</font>

1276
01:21:16,865 --> 01:21:19,785
<font color="#ffff00">We will rise to meet him.</font>

1277
01:21:23,425 --> 01:21:25,105
<font color="#ffff00">Let us pray.</font>

1278
01:21:30,185 --> 01:21:31,663
<font color="#ffffff">PRAYS SOFTLY</font>

1279
01:21:31,665 --> 01:21:33,265
<font color="#ffffff">MOTHER SUPERIOR: </font><font color="#ffff00">Ahem. Ahem.</font>

1280
01:21:34,745 --> 01:21:36,705
<font color="#ffffff">BLADE SLICES</font>

1281
01:21:38,425 --> 01:21:40,583
<font color="#ffffff">She was clearing her throat.</font>

1282
01:21:40,585 --> 01:21:42,505
<font color="#ffffff">NUNS GASP AND QUIVER</font>

1283
01:21:43,865 --> 01:21:45,785
<font color="#ffffff">I think it's fine now.</font>

1284
01:21:49,905 --> 01:21:53,585
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, ladies, who's next? Boo!</font>

1285
01:21:54,945 --> 01:21:56,345
<font color="#ffffff">ALL SCREAM</font>

1286
01:21:59,025 --> 01:22:01,823
<font color="#ffffff">HOWLING AND SNARLING</font>

1287
01:22:01,825 --> 01:22:05,143
<font color="#ffffff">It's just that I have a very hard</font>
<font color="#ffffff">time deciding who's going to be...</font>

1288
01:22:05,145 --> 01:22:06,263
<font color="#ffffff">NUNS SCREAM</font>

1289
01:22:06,265 --> 01:22:07,865
<font color="#ffffff">Here's an idea.</font>

1290
01:22:10,065 --> 01:22:11,703
<font color="#ffffff">Catch!</font>

1291
01:22:11,705 --> 01:22:13,063
<font color="#ffffff">NUNS SCREAM</font>

1292
01:22:13,065 --> 01:22:14,783
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMING CONTINUES</font>

1293
01:22:14,785 --> 01:22:16,463
<font color="#00ffff">This will be the safest spot.</font>

1294
01:22:16,465 --> 01:22:18,383
<font color="#00ff00">What is this place?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">My workshop.</font>

1295
01:22:18,385 --> 01:22:19,943
<font color="#00ffff">Here.</font>

1296
01:22:19,945 --> 01:22:22,023
<font color="#00ffff">Here. Where the sunlight hits.</font>

1297
01:22:22,025 --> 01:22:23,623
<font color="#00ff00">It's night-time.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">In the morning.</font>

1298
01:22:23,625 --> 01:22:25,303
<font color="#00ffff">In the morning.</font>

1299
01:22:25,305 --> 01:22:28,863
<font color="#00ff00">It's not morning for hours!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I know.</font>

1300
01:22:28,865 --> 01:22:30,463
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMING</font>

1301
01:22:30,465 --> 01:22:31,983
<font color="#ffffff">Who's got it?</font>

1302
01:22:31,985 --> 01:22:33,423
<font color="#ffffff">Who's caught it?</font>

1303
01:22:33,425 --> 01:22:35,783
<font color="#ffffff">Ah, we have a winner!</font>

1304
01:22:35,785 --> 01:22:37,303
<font color="#00ff00">What's that?</font>

1305
01:22:37,305 --> 01:22:39,183
<font color="#00ffff">Jesus.</font>

1306
01:22:39,185 --> 01:22:40,583
<font color="#00ff00">Jesus?</font>

1307
01:22:40,585 --> 01:22:41,823
<font color="#00ffff">Bread.</font>

1308
01:22:41,825 --> 01:22:44,025
<font color="#00ffff">Sacramental bread.</font>

1309
01:22:46,105 --> 01:22:47,945
<font color="#ffffff">WAILS</font>

1310
01:22:49,505 --> 01:22:51,943
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, of course.</font>

1311
01:22:51,945 --> 01:22:53,263
<font color="#ffffff">Nuns.</font>

1312
01:22:53,265 --> 01:22:56,663
<font color="#ffffff">You have those things,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">which work, actually,</font>

1313
01:22:56,665 --> 01:23:01,305
<font color="#ffffff">even though you will never...</font>

1314
01:23:02,705 --> 01:23:04,665
<font color="#ffffff">..guess why.</font>

1315
01:23:06,385 --> 01:23:08,063
<font color="#ffffff">EXHALES</font>

1316
01:23:08,065 --> 01:23:11,143
<font color="#ffffff">So I suppose</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'll just have to control myself.</font>

1317
01:23:11,145 --> 01:23:13,503
<font color="#ffffff">But, between you and me,</font>

1318
01:23:13,505 --> 01:23:16,583
<font color="#ffffff">controlling wolves</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is just so much more fun.</font>

1319
01:23:16,585 --> 01:23:18,343
<font color="#ffffff">BARKS AND SNARLS</font>

