01:23:18,345 --> 01:23:19,823
<font color="#ffffff">NUNS SCREAM</font>

1321
01:23:19,825 --> 01:23:24,063
<font color="#ffffff">It's a question of who you'd rather</font>
<font color="#ffffff">have tear you apart, I suppose.</font>

1322
01:23:24,065 --> 01:23:26,663
<font color="#ffffff">You have a choice, of course.</font>

1323
01:23:26,665 --> 01:23:28,463
<font color="#ffffff">I'm undead. I'm not unreasonable.</font>

1324
01:23:28,465 --> 01:23:30,183
