1328
01:23:37,905 --> 01:23:39,503
<font color="#ffffff">Ooh.</font>

1329
01:23:39,505 --> 01:23:42,263
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMING CONTINUES</font>

1330
01:23:42,265 --> 01:23:44,385
