1334
01:24:15,905 --> 01:24:17,823
<font color="#00ffff">It's all right. The screaming has</font>
<font color="#00ffff">stopped.</font>

1335
01:24:17,825 --> 01:24:19,863
<font color="#00ff00">Oh...</font>

1336
01:24:19,865 --> 01:24:22,663
<font color="#00ff00">..I don't know how you could bear</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to listen to that.</font>

1337
01:24:22,665 --> 01:24:26,305
<font color="#00ffff">I brought it on them.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Listening was my punishment.</font>

1338
01:24:29,985 --> 01:24:32,823
<font color="#00ff00">Dracula's going to find us, isn't</font>
<font color="#00ff00">he?</font>

1339
01:24:32,825 --> 01:24:34,023
<font color="#00ffff">Of course.</font>

1340
01:24:34,025 --> 01:24:36,863
<font color="#00ff00">How is bread going to keep him out?</font>

1341
01:24:36,865 --> 01:24:38,183
<font color="#00ffff">Sacramental bread.</font>

1342
01:24:38,185 --> 01:24:40,223
<font color="#00ff00">But how?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know.</font>

1343
01:24:40,225 --> 01:24:42,343
<font color="#00ffff">None of the vampire legends make</font>
<font color="#00ffff">sense,</font>

1344
01:24:42,345 --> 01:24:44,905
<font color="#00ffff">and yet somehow</font>
<font color="#00ffff">they are proving to be true.</font>

1345
01:24:45,945 --> 01:24:49,583
<font color="#00ffff">He can't enter a home</font>
<font color="#00ffff">without being invited. Why not?</font>

1346
01:24:49,585 --> 01:24:53,023
<font color="#00ffff">The light of the day</font>
<font color="#00ffff">would burn him to death. Why?</font>

1347
01:24:53,025 --> 01:24:56,623
<font color="#00ffff">He's terrified of the cross,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and yet he's no believer.</font>

1348
01:24:56,625 --> 01:25:00,703
<font color="#00ffff">Somehow, these facts</font>
<font color="#00ffff">are all the same fact.</font>

1349
01:25:00,705 --> 01:25:03,543
<font color="#00ffff">There's one thing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that Dracula fears above all</font>

1350
01:25:03,545 --> 01:25:05,145
<font color="#00ffff">and, to destroy him...</font>

1351
01:25:06,185 --> 01:25:07,905
<font color="#00ffff">...we must discover it.</font>

1352
01:25:09,665 --> 01:25:12,663
<font color="#00ff00">He got into the convent.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">How did he get in here?</font>

1353
01:25:12,665 --> 01:25:15,663
<font color="#00ffff">Well, clearly, there was an</font>
<font color="#00ffff">invitation.</font>

1354
01:25:15,665 --> 01:25:18,023
