<font color="#ffff00">I let him inside.</font>

1364
01:25:57,385 --> 01:26:00,023
<font color="#ffff00">He's inside.</font>

1365
01:26:00,025 --> 01:26:02,383
<font color="#00ff00">We know, Johnny.</font>

1366
01:26:02,385 --> 01:26:03,985
<font color="#00ff00">He killed everyone.</font>

1367
01:26:05,945 --> 01:26:07,823
<font color="#00ffff">Do not cross that line.</font>

1368
01:26:07,825 --> 01:26:09,303
<font color="#00ffff">You can't come any closer.</font>

1369
01:26:09,305 --> 01:26:12,783
<font color="#00ff00">Let him in.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We cannot trust him.</font>

1370
01:26:12,785 --> 01:26:15,423
<font color="#00ff00">He is strong, stronger than you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">think, and if I'm with him...</font>

1371
01:26:15,425 --> 01:26:16,703
<font color="#00ffff">No-one is strong enough.</font>

1372
01:26:16,705 --> 01:26:18,103
<font color="#00ffff">No-one! </font><font color="#00ff00">Please!</font>

1373
01:26:18,105 --> 01:26:21,985
<font color="#00ff00">We can't just leave him out there.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Do not invite him in!</font>

1374
01:26:25,785 --> 01:26:27,185
<font color="#00ff00">No!</font>

1375
01:26:33,145 --> 01:26:34,745
<font color="#00ff00">Come here, Johnny.</font>

1376
01:26:35,905 --> 01:26:37,345
<font color="#00ff00">Come to me.</font>

1377
01:26:38,705 --> 01:26:42,903
<font color="#00ff00">I am inviting you to be with us.</font>

1378
01:26:42,905 --> 01:26:44,743
<font color="#00ffff">You don't know what you're doing!</font>

1379
01:26:44,745 --> 01:26:46,823
<font color="#00ffff">He let Dracula in - he will do it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">again!</font>

1380
01:26:46,825 --> 01:26:49,663
<font color="#00ff00">You won't, will you, Johnny?</font>

1381
01:26:49,665 --> 01:26:51,223
<font color="#00ff00">Cos I'm here with you.</font>

1382
01:26:51,225 --> 01:26:53,663
<font color="#00ff00">And I will give you strength.</font>

1383
01:26:53,665 --> 01:26:56,865
<font color="#00ff00">The two of us, together,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">we can be stronger than...</font>

1384
01:27:01,905 --> 01:27:04,345
<font color="#00ff00">Johnny, your eyes...</font>

1385
01:27:06,145 --> 01:27:08,263
<font color="#ffff00">He's inside.</font>

